name: Bulbasaur
pokedex: It carries a seed on its back since birth. As it grows older, the seed also grows larger. It is known to be a well-behaved and loyal Pokémon, but pretty rare to find in the wild.
evolution_method: Evolves after reaching a certain level

name: Ivysaur
pokedex: There is a bud on this Pokémon's back. To support its weight, Ivysaur's legs and trunk grow thick and strong. It becomes kind of a loner after evolving and may stray away from its group to take sunbathes.
evolution_method: Evolves after reaching a certain level

name: Venusaur
pokedex: Venusaur's flower is said to take on vivid colors if it gets plenty of sunlight. The flower's aroma soothes the emotions of others. If you find one in the wild, it must be the protector of the area.

name: Charmander
pokedex: A rare Pokémon. The flame on its tail is an indicator of its feelings and life force. If it is healthy and happy, the flame burns brightly. It needs proper care and discipline or else it may rebel later on.
evolution_method: Evolves after reaching a certain level.

name: Charmeleon
pokedex: It turns aggressive after evolving. It is very hot-headed by nature, so it constantly starts fights. When it's excited, the flame at the tip of its tail flares with a bluish white color.
evolution_method: Evolves after reaching a certain level.

name: Charizard
pokedex: A Charizard flies around looking for strong opponents. It breathes intense flames that can melt any material. However, it will never touch a weaker foe. Not many trainers are able to handle its bad temper.

name: Squirtle
pokedex: It is scarce in the wild. The shell is not just for protection, it also helps to minimize resistance in water, enabling Squirtle to swim at high speeds. It's usually a calm and easygoing Pokémon.
evolution_method: Evolves after reaching a certain level.

name: Wartortle
pokedex: Its large tail is covered with rich, thick fur that deepens in color with age. The scratches on its shell are evidence of this Pokémon's tough attitude in battle. It is a good hunter underwater.
evolution_method: Evolves after reaching a certain level.

name: Blastoise
pokedex: The jets of water it spouts from the rocket cannons on its shell have been recorded to punch through steel. It is confident on its great defense and water spouts to overcome any obstacle.

name: Caterpie
pokedex: It is very common in the forests. Its voracious appetite compels it to devour leaves bigger than itself without hesitation. It releases a foul odor from its antennae if it feels threatened.

name: Metapod
pokedex: Its shell can be as hard as an iron slab. A Metapod does not move very much because it is preparing its soft innards for evolution inside the shell. It is known as one of the fastest evolving Pokémon in the world.
evolution_method: Evolves after 7 days in this form.

name: Butterfree
pokedex: It can be found in forests and plains. It loves the honey in some flowers even with tiny amounts of pollen. Its wings are covered by dust that allows it to fly even when it's raining.

name: Weedle
pokedex: Often found in forests eating leaves. It has a sharp, venomous stinger on its head for defense. It has an acute sense of smell to find food and its bright-colored body is intended to warn off predators.

name: Kakuna
pokedex: It remains virtually immobile while it clings to a tree. On the inside, it is preparing for evolution by raising the temperature of its shell. Beware of Beedrills that may roam close to it.
evolution_method: Evolves after 10 days in this form.

name: Beedrill
pokedex: A Beedrill is extremely territorial. For safety reasons, no one should ever approach their nest. If it is disturbed, they will attack in a swarm. It has three stingers and the one on its tail secretes a powerful poison.

name: Pidgey
pokedex: Very common around the world, it prefers to live in forests but can be seen around cities and plains, as well. It's a docile Pokémon that tends to avoid trouble. It flaps its wings to lure prey out of hiding.
evolution_method: Evolves after honing its flight skills.

name: Pidgeotto
pokedex: Each Pidgeotto claims a large area around meadows as its territory. This Pokémon flies around, patrolling its home, and will attack any intruders with its sharp claws. It will challenge itself to fly a bit higher every day.
evolution_method: Evolves after honing its flight skills.

name: Pidgeot
pokedex: This Pokémon's plumage is made of beautiful glossy feathers. Pidgeot is an excellent hunter with well developed wing muscles that make it strong enough to whip up a gusty windstorm with just a few flaps.

name: Rattata
pokedex: It can live anywhere it can find food, but they are often found in cities and fields. They form large families in their burrows. Since they are often preyed on, Rattatas are always alert and quick to flee.

name: Rattata (Alola)
pokedex: Rattata first came to Alola through cargo ships. It thrived and almost destroyed the region's ecosystem. Attempts to exterminate this Pokémon made it more vicious than its regular counterpart.

name: Raticate
pokedex: Raticate's study fangs grow quickly. To keep them ground down, it gnaws on hard materials and it may even chew on the walls of houses. It has waterproof fur, webbed feet, and it a capable swimmer.

name: Raticate (Alola)
pokedex: Alolan Raticate command their Rattata underlings to bring them food every night. Five star restaurants often struggle with these aggressive Pokémon nesting close to their grounds.

name: Spearow
pokedex: It lives in flocks on grasslands and is very protective of its territory. It flaps its short wings to dart around at high speed. Spearows are a little short-tempered; if disturbed, it will shriek, calling its flock for aid.
evolution_method: Evolves by being dominant in the flock.

name: Fearow
pokedex: Fearows soar around wastelands and fields. They have the stamina to fly all day, but they are ill-tempered and easily annoyed. They attack using their sharp beak to peck and pierce their foes.

name: Ekans
pokedex: It is often found in grasslands, preying on Rattatas and Pokémon Eggs it finds. Its jaw can detach itself to swallow any prey whole. After eating, it coils up to sleep. As Ekans ages, it continues growing bigger.
evolution_method: Evolves after reaching a certain size.

name: Arbok
pokedex: This Pokémon has an incredibly strong constricting power. Once it wraps its body around its foe, escaping is almost impossible. The pattern on its body glows in the dark like a terrifying face.

name: Pikachu
pokedex: Pikachu lives in small groups in forests, but they tend to stay hidden. It stores electricity in the electric sacs on its cheeks and uses its tail to ground the excess charge. They can be stubborn and wary of strangers.

name: Raichu
pokedex: When electricity builds on its body, it starts to emit a faint glow and it becomes more aggressive than it normally is. They live in forests but are rare to find in the wild.

name: Raichu (Alola)
pokedex: Scientists were baffled to discover Raichu's evolution in the Alola Region. There is no explanation as to how it gained Psychic abilities, but diet seems to be a factor. It loves sweet food and pancakes.

name: Sandshrew
pokedex: The usually hide burrowed under caves and grasslands. A few have been sighted living in the desert. They are shy by nature - they dig and curl in a ball when facing a threat.
evolution_method: Evolves after reaching a certain level.

name: Sandshrew (Alola)
pokedex: Sandshrew who become trapped in the merciless cold weather of Alola had to change their types to survive. They now depend on snow to roll around, without it, they are unable to curl up into a ball.

name: Sandslash
pokedex: It's less shy than its first stage. It curls up in a ball to protect itself from enemy attacks. Surprisingly, it is a good climber that uses its sharp claws for grip and drilling tunnels underground.

name: Sandslash (Alola)
pokedex: These Pokémon make their burrows on Alola's ice caverns, hidden in plain sight. Careful with its spikes, any puncture into the skin and you can get severe frostbite. They can't stand high temperatures.

name: Nidoran ♀
pokedex: A female only species. It lives close to meadows and forests. They are mellow Pokémon. To protect herself, she secretes a powerful toxin through her body. Her horn is small but venomous to the touch.

name: Nidorina
pokedex: Nidorina are jealous creatures. They don't like other females near their mates. Otherwise, they are very social creatures. When it's around friends and family, its barbs are tucked away to prevent injury.

name: Nidoqueen
pokedex: Motherly by nature, it uses its scaly rugged body to seal the entrance of its nest and protect its young from predators. There are records of angry Nidoqueens sending people flying with a single tackle.

name: Nidoran ♂
pokedex: The male Nidoran has developed a great alertness to sounds. Its small body is covered in spikes that are drenched in venom when he's threatened. He will defend his mate and home fiercely.

name: Nidorino
pokedex: An independent and fierce creature. It roams alone in search for a mate and will compete with other males around. It will violently charge with a venom drenched horn against intruders.

name: Nidoking
pokedex: It is recognized by its rock-hard hide and its extended horn. Be careful with the horn as it contains venom. There are records of one trampling and destroying a radio tower that was built on his territory.

name: Clefairy
pokedex: Very rare to find. Clefairy are said to come from the moon. They are drawn to the light of this celestial body and come out of hiding at night to dance and play in the moonlight.

name: Clefable
pokedex: There are not many records about it in the wild. They are timid but playful. Clefable uses its wings to skip lightly as if it was flying. Its bouncy step lets it walk on water. On quiet, moonlit nights, it strolls near lakes.

name: Vulpix
pokedex: It is born with just one tail. As it grows, its single white tail gains color and splits into six. It is quite warm and cuddly - a very popular pet. It is, however, uncommon to see one in the wild.

name: Vulpix (Alola)
pokedex: The Vulpix who became stranded in Alola had to change type in order to survive. Alola's local name for this Pokémon is Keokeo. They use their tails as a fan to cool themselves in hot climates.

name: Ninetails
pokedex: It is known to understand human speech. It is very valued for its exuberant golden fur and the mystical power of its nine tails. It is, however, known to hold a grudge against those who mistreat it.

name: Ninetails (Alola)
pokedex: In olde times, Alolan natives revered this Pokémon as a god incarnate. It is usually calm and benevolent, but it can be ruthless when disturbed, leaving its foes as a cold block of ice in the snow.

name: Jigglypuff
pokedex: They live in grassy fields near the mountains. To climb, they inflate their bodies and bounce up. It captivates foes with its huge round eyes, then lulls them to sleep by singing a sweet soothing melody.

name: Wigglytuff
pokedex: Its fur is extremely fine and conveys an image of luxury. Its body is soft and rubbery. When angered, it will suck the air and inflate itself to an enormous size. It is a favorite pet and a nurse Pokémon.

name: Zubat
pokedex: It lives in dark caves all around the world. Prolonged exposure to the sun will make it unhealthy. It is blind but uses echolocation to find its way. At night, they leave their cave to feed on fruit and bug Pokémon.
evolution_method: Evolves after reaching a certain level.

name: Golbat
pokedex: A stealthy Pokémon who loves the dark. Its fangs can puncture even a thick hide. It loves to feast on the blood of people and Pokémon alike. If it drinks too much, it gets heavy and can hardly fly.

name: Oddish
pokedex: This Pokémon grows by absorbing moonlight. During daytime, it buries itself in the ground, leaving only its leaves exposed to avoid detection by predators. You can locate it by the smell its leaves release.
evolution_method: Evolves after reaching a certain size.

name: Gloom
pokedex: A horribly noxious honey drools from its mouth. One whiff of the honey can result in sickness. Some fans are said to enjoy its overwhelming stink though. You can control this foul smell with lots of love and care.
evolution_method: Evolves with a Leaf Stone or Sun Stone.

name: Vileplume
pokedex: It lives in marshlands and jungles where it's often mistaken for local flora. The air around a Vileplume turns yellow with the powder it releases as it walks. The pollen is highly toxic and causes paralysis.

name: Paras
pokedex: Paras has two parasitic mushrooms growing on its back. They grow large by drawing nutrients from this Bug Pokémon. They are valued as a medicine for prolonging life. Paras can be found in humid areas.
evolution_method: Evolves if its mushroom grows too big.

name: Parasect
pokedex: It lives in marshlands and jungles where it's often mistaken for local flora. The air around a Vileplume turns yellow with the powder it releases as it walks. The pollen is highly toxic and causes paralysis.

name: Venonat
pokedex: It lives in the holes of trees in dense forests and jungles. Its large eyes never fail to spot even miniscule prey. Sometimes Venonat uses its powers to confuse travelers and make them lose their way.
evolution_method: Evolves after reaching a certain level.

name: Venomoth
pokedex: They are plentiful in forests but only come out at night. They possess an incredible eyesight and are attracted to light sources. Their wings scatter a toxic powder which they use to immobilize their prey.

name: Diglett
pokedex: It prefers dark places and spends most of its time underground. It has very thin skin. It's frail and has problems regulating its own temperature. Keep it burrowed or it will get sick.
evolution_method: Evolves after reaching a certain size.

name: Diglett (Alola)
pokedex: This variant of Diglett is only found in the Alola region. The small hairs on its head are used to perceive its surroundings while burrowed. Do not cut them or Diglett will become very sick.
evolution_method: Evolves by taking good care of its hair.

name: Dugtrio
pokedex: Because the triplets originally split from one body, they think exactly alike. They work together to dig endlessly through the ground. They are known for destroying the foundations of roads and buildings.

name: Dugtrio (Alola)
pokedex: Thanks to its golden mane, this Pokémon has been revered as a feminine deity. The triplets groom each other to keep the hair glossy and dirt-free. They don't like to be petted.

name: Meowth
pokedex: The used to live in grasslands, but have adapted well to life in the city. Shiny things fascinate them and they keep a little treasure hidden. The coin on its head is its most prized possession.
evolution_method: Evolves when its surrounded by riches.

name: Meowth (Alola)
pokedex: In old times, Meowth were taken to Alola as gifts for the tribe's royals. This caused them to become incredibly greedy and pampered. Nowadays, they are feral, but their prideful nature remained.

name: Persian
pokedex: They are proud and temperamental. They scratch their trainers with little to no provocation whatsoever. Their elegance and grace is very valued, although they can be vicious hunters.

name: Persian (Alola)
pokedex: They were bred for their silky fur and round faces, not for their temperament. This is an extremely proud Pokémon, who will look down on anyone but itself, despite this, it's very popular amongst Alola's elite.

name: Psyduck
pokedex: It lives near lakes and ponds, but it's not very good at swimming. It is always tormented by headaches that worsen when it uses psychic powers. Psyducks seem unaware of their own power.
evolution_method: Evolves by learning to control its powers.

name: Golduck
pokedex: A Golduck is an adept swimmer and can be found near most bodies of water. Its forehead shimmers with light when using its psychic abilities. There are records of wild Golducks that rescued people in the water.

name: Mankey
pokedex: It lives on the mountains or at the top of fruit trees. Light and agile on its feet and ferocious in temperament. When it gets angry, it goes into a frenzy and cannot be controlled.
evolution_method: Evolves after a terrible temper tantrum.

name: Primeape
pokedex: It grows angry if you look in its eyes and gets angrier if you run. If you fight it will go mad with rage. Not many trainers are capable of handling it, the angrier it gets, the less intelligent it becomes.

name: Growlithe
pokedex: Friendly, loyal and fearless to defend its trainer. These traits have gained them a place working as police Pokémon. They are uncommon in the wild, but some packs can be seen in hot environments.

name: Arcanine
pokedex: Its proud and regal appearance has made it revered by people of ancient societies. Its magnificent bark conveys a sense of majesty. Anyone in front of Arcanine can't help but stare in awe.

name: Poliwag
pokedex: They are most common near ponds and lakes during the summer. Its legs take some weeks to develop after it hatches, making it inept at walking. It is, however, a very fast swimmer.
evolution_method: Evolves after reaching a certain level.

name: Poliwhirl
pokedex: Though it is skilled at walking, it prefers to live underwater, where there's less danger. It sweats to keep its skin moist. Thanks to this, it can easily slip out of the clutches of any enemy.

name: Poliwrath
pokedex: It's not common to find it in the wild. Many sightings take place when it is on land. Once he is inside the water, it will swim far away. This Pokémon is an outstanding swimmer, capable of beating any human.

name: Abra
pokedex: They are attracted to the cities and tend to live close to humans. Its Psychic abilities are still developing, it must sleep a lot, up to 18 hours a day, in order to use them. When in danger, it teleports away.
evolution_method: Evolves by learning to control its powers

name: Kadabra
pokedex: Kadabra holds a silver spoon in its hand. The spoon is used to amplify the alpha waves of its brain. When this Pokémon walks in, objects near to it go crazy, moving in ways they shouldn't.

name: Alakazam
pokedex: A Pokémon that can memorize anything and never forgets what it learns. Over time, it becomes too smart to allow anyone to be its master. Alakazam's psychic powers can be terrifying.

name: Machop
pokedex: It lives in mountains, training its fists against strong rocks, lifting boulders, and hurling Rock Pokémon around to build stronger muscles. Even with its small size, it can compete against expert humans and win.
evolution_method: Evolves after reaching a certain level.

name: Machoke
pokedex: Even with its strong frame and power, it is a humble and helpful Pokémon. Many of them work for human companies. On their days off, you can see them heading to the wild to train together.

name: Machamp
pokedex: There are a few roaming in the mountains. Machamp has the power to hurl anything aside. However, trying to do any work that requires care and dexterity may cause its arms to get tangled.

name: Bellsprout
pokedex: They live in hot and humid places, blending around with the flora. It is carnivorous and will try to eat anything smaller than itself. It digests its prey with an acid substance it its head.
evolution_method: Evolves after reaching a certain size.

name: Weepinbell
pokedex: It sprays its stun powder to immobilize a prey coming close to it, then its it calmly. If the prey is bigger than itself, it uses its sharp leaves to slice it into smaller pieces. Beware of the toxic liquid in its mouth.

name: Victreebel
pokedex: They live together in small groups at tropical areas. Victreebel uses a sweet honey-like smell to lure and attract prey. They also use their long vines to rustle bushes around. They are very territorial and aggressive.

name: Tentacool
pokedex: It lives in the seas all around the world. They release a toxic ink if startled. It is a surprisingly intelligent Pokémon and can use its tentacles to briefly establish a link between its mind and another creature.
evolution_method: Evolves after reaching a certain size.

name: Tentacruel
pokedex: Lives in rock formations at the bottom of the ocean. It can grow tentacles at will and uses them to immobilize prey. Records exist of a giant Tentacruel that sunk a fleet of pirate ships filled with treasure.

name: Geodude
pokedex: Lives in mountains and caves. It looks indistinguishable from other rocks around. Because of this, many trainers step on them and are attacked. It rolls to move around and eats whatever it finds on the floor.
evolution_method: Evolves after reaching a certain size.

name: Geodude (Alola)
pokedex: The magnetic fields on Alola's Blush Mountain made Geodude develop Electric charges on its body. They tend to disguise themselves as regular rocks. Caution is advised as they shock you if you step on them.
evolution_method: Evolves after reaching a certain size.

name: Graveler
pokedex: It walks slowly, but it can get a nice speed by rolling downhill. It is good at climbing. Groups of them have been seen clinging from rock formations and cliffs to eat the tasty rocks covered in moss.

name: Graveler (Alola)
pokedex: These Pokémon charge themselves by rolling around. It is dangerous if two of them collide. If that happens a loud noise and a flash of light will be seen and heard at great distance. They feed on golden dravite.

name: Golem
pokedex: It is rare to see in the wild, since it lives high on the mountains. It withdraws its head and legs as if it were a turtle to roll around. There have been cases of Golems who resist dynamite blasts unscathed.

name: Golem (Alola)
pokedex: The Alolan variant of Golem does not roll around like its counterpart, instead it loads rocks into its charger on its head and shoots them around. If the rocks miss, the electric shockwave doesn't.

name: Ponyta
pokedex: It's not very common to see one stay still for more than a few seconds. Soon after it's born, its flames begin to burn. It is weak at first, but soon begins to develop at great speed, chasing after its parents.
evolution_method: Evolves after reaching a certain level.

name: Rapidash
pokedex: It lives happily on prairies. It loves speed competitions - a herd can often be seen running alongside a train. It can regulate the heat of its mane as to let its trainer ride it, but only if it trusts him enough.

name: Slowpoke
pokedex: It lives close to water. This Pokémon has a low intellect, and it's slow to react to any stimuli. Its tail seeps a sweet substance it uses to lure prey to eat. When the tip turns white, shellders will be attracted to it.
evolution_method: Evolves by natural means and trade holding an item.

name: Slowbro
pokedex: This Pokémon fused with a Shellder that it into its tail. It's a slow swimmer and doesn't react to pain, but Shellder tends to keep it out of trouble.
evolution_method: It lives in marshlands and jungles where it's often mistaken for local flora. The air around a Vileplume turns yellow with the powder it releases as it walks. The pollen is highly toxic and causes paralysis.

name: Magnemite
pokedex: It lurks near electric facilities and mountains as it is attracted by big magnetic fields. It is not aggressive and usually defends itself with a screech or a weak electric impulse to deter others from attacking.
evolution_method: Evolves around a strong Magnetic Field.

name: Magneton
pokedex: Sometimes three Magnemites fuse into this Pokémon, other times a single one sprouts two others. This species is greatly affected by magnetic fields. Magnetons are eager to please their trainers.
evolution_method: Evolves around a strong Magnetic Field.

name: Farfetch'd
pokedex: There used to be whole flocks of them in meadows near the lakes. Now they are almost extinct because their meat is delicious. They are fond of leeks and celery, they carry them around as sticks.

name: Doduo
pokedex: It can jump so high and land so delicately that it's almost as if it is able to fly, but it prefers to run in the prairies. The two heads usually get along. While one is eating and sleeping, the other one is alert for predators. It is known that they share a brain and their ideas are connected.
evolution_method: Evolves after reaching a certain level.

name: Dodrio
pokedex: A third head comes to change the dynamic the two original heads had. It is common to see the three heads fighting. Each one has its own personality, but when they work as a team they can be very powerful.

name: Seel
pokedex: A Pokémon that lives on icebergs. It swims in the sea using the point of its head to break up the ice. It sleeps a lot during the day, being most active at dawn when the temperature starts to cool.
evolution_method: Evolves after reaching a certain level.

name: Dewgong
pokedex: Its body is covered with a pure white fur. The colder the weather, the more active it becomes. It hunts at night and it's excellent at catching fish Pokémon. It is also very intelligent and playful.

name: Grimer
pokedex: It was born from polluted sludge in the sea. Grimer's favorite food is anything filthy, like waste water pumped out from factories. Grime and sludge stick to their body making them grow larger over time.
evolution_method: Evolves after reaching a certain size.

name: Grimer (Alola)
pokedex: Grimer were brought into Alola to eat garbage on the region. It seemed like a counterintuitive measure, but ended up solving the problem. However, the Alolan garbage made Alolan Grimer incredibly toxic, much more toxic than usual.
evolution_method: Evolves after reaching a certain size.

name: Muk
pokedex: It gathers on polluted areas to eat filth. Its body is made of a powerful poison that kills any plant. Touching it can cause a fever that will require bed rest. A good diet may reduce Muk's toxicity.

name: Muk (Alola)
pokedex: It is as friendly as it is toxic, be careful, for it tries to hug others regularly. A good diet does not help reduce its toxicity levels, it only makes it cranky and prone to destroy furniture. It releases toxic fumes all the time.

name: Shellder
pokedex: It lives at the bottom of the sea and rivers. It feeds on algae and it's attracted to sweet substances. When frightened, it will shut its shell and lock it to be almost impossible to open.

name: Cloyster
pokedex: If it lives in seas with harsh currents, it will grow larger and sharper spikes on its shells than those who live on calm waters. Its shell is extremely hard - you would need explosives to try and open it.

name: Gastly
pokedex: Its body is made of a toxic gas - anyone would faint if engulfed by it. It has been seen in abandoned places, scaring people and other Pokémon for fun. It is elusive and escapes through the walls.
evolution_method: Evolves after reaching a certain size.

name: Haunter
pokedex: Haunter is a dangerous Pokémon. It will try to lick you with its tongue to steal your life away. If you get the feeling of being watched in the darkness when nobody is around, it means a Haunter is there.

name: Gengar
pokedex: This Pokémon is mischievous, so much so that it can be downright evil. It takes joy in casting curses upon innocents and eating the life of people and Pokémon. It lurks in the shadows and disguises itself as one.

name: Onix
pokedex: It is not full-size when it is born. Years of eating boulders make it a real giant. It lives on mountains and dark tunnels. It's frightening roars travel as echoes through the cave. It is very aggressive towards others.
evolution_method: Evolves with high pressure, iron, and heat.

name: Drowzee
pokedex: It eats the dreams of a sleeping person or Pokémon and particularly enjoys eating the dreams of young children. Once the victim is deep in slumber, it will extract and eat the dream through the nose.
evolution_method: Evolves after eating the greatest dream.

name: Hypno
pokedex: Old stories tell of a Hypno who takes away naughty children and feasts on their dreams until they are old. They have an urge to eat dreams of others since they cannot sleep themselves.

name: Krabby
pokedex: A Krabby digs holes in the sand near the sea. They can be seen squabbling with each other over food and territory. They usually avoid humans, but will fight if provoked.
evolution_method: Evolves after reaching a certain level.

name: Kingler
pokedex: Its pincers grow peculiarly large. If it lifts the pincers too fast, it may lose its balance and stagger. If one of its pincers is damaged, it will detach from its body. It will regrow after a few days.

name: Voltorb
pokedex: They live near factories and electric generators. It bears an uncanny and unexplained resemblance to a Pokeball. Since it explodes at the slightest provocation, even veteran trainers treat it with caution.
evolution_method: Evolves after a terrible temper tantrum.

name: Electrode
pokedex: It is known for causing blackouts in the cities. After evolving, it explodes as a way to release excess electricity or simply to amuse itself. Trainers need to be careful around an Electrode.

name: Exeggcute
pokedex: Even though it appears to be eggs of some sort, it is related more to a seed. It gathers in packs of six that have a mental link with each other. Each one of them has a different personality.

name: Exeggutor
pokedex: Originally from tropical areas, Exeggutor heads grow larger with strong sunlight. Each head thinks independently. They are friendly and provide their shade to other Pokémon.

name: Exeggutor (Alola)
pokedex: Alola is the native region for this Pokémon, only there can it evolve into this form. With its size, its Psychic abilities are rarely needed and its trainers order's rarely heard. They enjoy the sun in the beach.

name: Cubone
pokedex: Cubone wears a skull helmet it never removes. It is said to be from its mother or someone dear to it. Lives in the mountains where it cries at night due to the sadness it feels. It is distrustful of humans.

name: Marowak
pokedex: Its rough past has hardened its heart. Now tenacious and violent, this Pokémon will use its Bone club as a weapon against foes. Marowak's den is usually full of the bones it has collected.

name: Marowak (Alola)
pokedex: Alola has many predators for an orphaned Cubone, so its mother's spirit lingered close to protect her baby. This otherworldly influence made Marowak fiercer and change its type completely.

name: Hitmonlee
pokedex: Its legs freely stretch and contract. It bowls over foes with devastating kicks. It is very disciplined and trainse every day. It is very rare in the wild, and it is mostly found in urban areas.

name: Hitmonchan
pokedex: It specializes in punching as fast as it can. Using a corkscrew motion, it can even drill through concrete with its bare hands. This Pokémon takes its training very seriously. It's very rare to see one in the wild.

name: Lickitung
pokedex: Its tongue is two times longer than its body and it is used for everything from capturing prey to feeling its surroundings and cleaning itself. It really dislikes sour and bitter flavors.

name: Koffing
pokedex: It is drawn to the smog and fumes of the cities. It fills its body with toxic gases to float like a balloon. When it gets nervous it releases a sickly green gas. Breathing this gas will give you a bad case of the sniffles.
evolution_method: Evolves after reaching a certain size.

name: Rhyhorn
pokedex: It lives in grasslands and rough terrains. It is covered with a thick hide and it tramples any threats by running towards them. It is not very smart though. It can keep trampling things for hours just because.
evolution_method: Evolves after reaching a certain level.

name: Weezing
pokedex: They are considered a pest in urban areas. They wait until night to roam and eat from the trash cans in the neighborhood. If it finds a filthy and unkempt house, it will make its nest there.

name: Rhydon
pokedex: It has a horn that serves as a drill for destroying rocks and boulders. Rhydon occasionally goes for a swim in rivers and even magma pools. It's great resistance prevents it from taking any damage.
evolution_method: Evolves after being traded while holding a certain item.

name: Chansey
pokedex: Chansey lays a nutritive egg every day. These eggs are fed to the sick to give them strength. It is a loving and smart Pokémon, but it's pretty rare and elusive in the wild.

name: Tangela
pokedex: It blends with foliage in jungle and forest areas. It's vines snap off easily and painlessly if they are grabbed, allowing it to make a quick getaway. The lost vines are replaced by new growth the very next day.
evolution_method: Evolves after contact with Primal Forces.

name: Kangaskhan
pokedex: It raises its offspring in its belly pouch. The young leaves once it learns to find its own food. In the wild, mothers and daughters fiercely defend each other.

name: Horsea
pokedex: It makes its nest in the shade of corals in shallow parts of the sea. If it senses danger it spits a murky ink and flees. It has been seen shooting down flying bugs to eat them.
evolution_method: Evolves after reaching a certain level.

name: Seadra
pokedex: The poisonous barbs all over its body are highly valued as ingredients for making traditional medicine. It will show no mercy if anything approaches its nest. Its back fin has a numbing substance.
evolution_method: Evolves after being traded holding a certain item.

name: Goldeen
pokedex: Goldeen loves swimming wild and free in rivers and ponds. If one of these Pokémon is placed in an aquarium it will shatter the glass with its horn and make its escape.
evolution_method: Evolves after reaching a certain level.

name: Seaking
pokedex: In the autumn, Seaking males can be seen doing courtship dances to females. After getting a mate, both will be seen swimming powerfully up rivers and creeks to make their nest.

name: Staryu
pokedex: They come to the shore in great numbers when the sky is full of stars. The core it its center glows to communicate with others. If a part of its body is injured it can regrow it in a few days.

name: Starmie
pokedex: This Pokémon has been given the nickname "the gem of the sea." It swims through water by spinning its star-shaped body as if it were a propeller on a ship. The core at the center glows with different colors.

name: Mr. Mime
pokedex: You don't find this Pokémon, it finds you. It is really smart and amuses itself by showing people its power to create barriers with pantomime. It creates an invisible box and flees when you try to figure out the exit.

name: Scyther
pokedex: It's pretty rare, but a few swarms have been seen in the grasslands. It tears and shreds prey with its wickedly sharp scythes and very rarely spreads its wings to fly. The Pokémon is stealthy and aggressive.
evolution_method: Evolves after being traded while holding a certain item.

name: Jynx
pokedex: It is not common outside of cold areas. This Pokémon is female only. Its cries sound like human speech. However, it is impossible to tell what it is trying to say. The way it moves and talks induce others to dance.

name: Electabuzz
pokedex: A violent Pokémon. It searches for spots where it can feed on electricity and has been seen absorbing lightning from the sky. It's competitive and aggressive with others.
evolution_method: Evolves after being traded holding a certain item.

name: Magmar
pokedex: It can be found living in volcanic areas. In battle, Magmar blows out intense flames all over its body to intimidate the opponent. This creates heat waves that ignite grass and trees in the surroundings.
evolution_method: Evolves after being traded holding a certain item.

name: Pinsir
pokedex: Their pincers are strong enough to shatter thick logs. Because they dislike cold, Pinsirs burrow and sleep under the ground on chilly nights. They like to eat sap and honey, but they are aggressive by nature.

name: Tauros
pokedex: They travel in herds around the plains and fight each other by locking horns. The herd's protector takes pride in its battle-scarred horns.

name: Magikarp
pokedex: Magikarp is a pathetic excuse of a Pokémon. It's not even good to eat. It's only capable of flopping and splashing. However, it can survive in any body of water no matter how polluted it is.
evolution_method: It is not know what makes it evolve.

name: Gyarados
pokedex: It's rarely seen in the wild. This huge and vicious Pokémon is known for the destruction it leaves in its wake. In ancient literature, there is a record of a Gyarados that razed a village when violence flared.

name: Lapras
pokedex: People have driven Lapras near the point of extinction. In the evenings, this Pokémon is said to sing as it seeks what few others of its kind still remain. Their gentle nature has made them easy to lure and catch.

name: Ditto
pokedex: This Pokémon is quite common, but it's pretty difficult to spot. It can transform into any other Pokémon and imitate their behavior. When it sleeps, it changes into a stone to avoid being attacked.

name: Eevee
pokedex: This Pokémon is extremely rare to find. Eevee has an unstable genetic makeup that suddenly mutates to fit its environment. Radiation from various stones causes this Pokémon to evolve.
evolution_method: Evolves through stones happiness and special conditions.

name: Vaporeon
pokedex: Vaporeon underwent through a strange mutation. It grew fins and gils that allow it to live underwater. This Pokémon has the ability to become translucent when it dives underwater.

name: Jolteon
pokedex: This Pokémon evolved after being affected by electric radiation. Every hair on its body starts to stand sharply if it becomes charged with electricity. It shoots lightning from all around its body.

name: Flareon
pokedex: A few have been seen in volcanic areas, but just like its other Eevee-based counterparts, is more common to see as a pet of a wealthy person. Its flaming fur is most appreciated for its warm glow and silky touch.

name: Porygon
pokedex: The first case of a man-made Pokémon created as computer data. It is capable of reverting itself into a program in order to enter cyberspace. Its software has a firewall so it cannot be copied.

name: Omanyte
pokedex: One of the ancient and extinct Pokémon that have been revived from fossils by science. If attacked, it withdraws into its hard shell. It is not found in the wild anymore, but fossils can be found in the sea.
evolution_method: Evolves after reaching a certain level.

name: Omastar
pokedex: An Omastar used its tentacles to ensnare and capture its prey. It is believed to have become extinct because the shell grew to large making it slow and ponderous. It is not found in the wild anymore.

name: Kabuto
pokedex: Kabuto is a Pokémon that has been regenerated from a fossil. However, in extremely rare cases, living specimens have been found. The Pokémon has not changed at all for 300 million years.
evolution_method: Evolves after reaching a certain level.

name: Kabutops
pokedex: Kabutops swarmed underwater to hunt for prey. It apparently evolved from a water dweller to living on land. It's evident from the changes in its gills and legs. Its fossils suggests it was aggressive.

name: Aerodactyl
pokedex: A vicious Pokémon from the distant past. It appears to have flown by spreading its wings and gliding. One has been revived from a fossil. It's very dangerous: it attacks with the intent to tear apart its victims.

name: Snorlax
pokedex: Snorlax's typical day consists of eating and sleeping. It is such a docile Pokémon that children use its big belly as a place to play. It only attacks when it's awoken harshly. Fortunately, it is a heavy sleeper.

name: Articuno
pokedex: Rumor has it that one appeared during a blizzard in front of two lost hikers who followed its glistening trial until they found the main road. Others say its silhouette can be seen during raging snow storms.

name: Zapdos
pokedex: The myth tells of a bird who lived inside the thunderstorms of the region. It covered itself in lightning while flying in the dark clouds. A news report said it was involved in the closure of an energy plant.

name: Moltres
pokedex: The legend speaks of a bird who came flying from the south. Its fiery body melted the snow and brought the spring along. A children's book depicts a similar Pokémon living inside a volcano.

name: Dratini
pokedex: Up until recently, its existence was debated as being a mere legend. Then a small colony was found underwater. It is still extremely rare to find. It sheds skin and grows large everyday.
evolution_method: Evolves after reaching a certain level.

name: Dragonair
pokedex: It is said to live in seas and lakes. Even though it has no wings, it has been depicted as flying. There were legends of this Pokémon controlling the weather and ending the storms to leave a rainbow behind.

name: Dragonite
pokedex: Very few people have ever seen this Pokémon. Its intelligence matches that of humans. There are records of a Pokémon with a similar description that helped rescue a ship full of people during a hurricane.

name: Mewtwo
pokedex: An article in a science magazine talked about how much the cloning research was progressing, but...could it be?

name: Mew
pokedex: Recent investigations declare that this Pokémon could be the common ancestor of all actual Pokémon, but it has been extinct for centuries. Some people claim to have seen one to get their 15 minutes of fame.

name: Chikorita
pokedex: It is docile and loves to bathe in the sunlight. It waves its leaf around to keep foes at bay. The sweet fragrance from its leaf has a strong calming and relaxing effect on people and Pokémon.
evolution_method: Evolves after reaching a certain level.

name: Bayleef
pokedex: A spicy fragrance emanates from around its neck that makes it feisty and impetuous. It sheds its outer leaves every couple of weeks after the aroma diminishes and its mood also becomes calmer.
evolution_method: Evolves after reaching a certain level.

name: Meganium
pokedex: Maganium's breath has the power to revive dead grass and plants. The aroma that comes from its petals contains a substance that calms aggressive feelings and helps others to restore health.

name: Cyndaquil
pokedex: A shy and elusive Pokémon. The flames from its back protect it. They'll burn vigorously if Cyndaquil is angry, otherwise they'll remain unlit. It lives in hot dens inside of mountains and volcanoes.
evolution_method: Evolves after reaching a certain level.

name: Quilava
pokedex: It intimidates foes with intense gusts of flames and superheated air. Beware: if Quilava turns its back, it is planning on using a fire move.
evolution_method: Evolves after reaching a certain level.

name: Typhlosion
pokedex: Very rare to see in the wild. It hides behind a shimmering heat haze created using its fire. Typhlosion can create eruptions and explosive blasts that can burn everything to the ground.

name: Totodile
pokedex: Despite its small body, Totodile's jaws are very powerful. While it may think it is just playfully nipping, its bite has enough strength to cause a serious injury. It needs proper discipline to control its biting urges.
evolution_method: Evolves after reaching a certain level.

name: Croconaw
pokedex: This Pokémon is really tenacious. Once it bites something, it won't let go until it tears it down - even if its trainer is ordering to let go. If it loses any of its fangs, they'll regrow in a few days. It's a very wild Pokémon.
evolution_method: Evolves after reaching a certain level.

name: Feraligatr
pokedex: While in the water, it opens its big jaw to intimidate anyone coming close. Whenever it bites, it shakes its head and savagely rolls to tear up its prey. It is a very dangerous Pokémon. Approach with caution.

name: Sentret
pokedex: It lives underground with its family. It is cautious and nervous by nature. Sentret is always vigilant for any threat. It is very friendly among its kind and suffers a lot of separated from its pack.
evolution_method: Evolves after reaching a certain level.

name: Furret
pokedex: It lives along its Sentret family and acts as the hunter and caregiver of the pack. It can move really fast. If it is cornered, it will squirm through even the narrowest of gaps to escape safe and sound.

name: Hoothoot
pokedex: A nocturnal Pokémon found in dark forests. It has an internal organ that senses the earth's rotation. By using this special organ a Hoot-hoot begins hooting at precisely the same time every day.
evolution_method: Evolves after reaching a certain level.

name: Noctowl
pokedex: It can hunt in full darkness without fail. All Noctowls owe their success to their superior vision - that allows them to see in minimal light, and to their agile and silent wings. They are very intelligent and critical Pokémon.

name: Ledyba
pokedex: These timid Pokémon swarm in groups to keep each other warm during the winter. It communicates with others through a special scent. They often appear covered in morning dew.

name: Ledian
pokedex: When the stars flicker in the night sky, it flutters about scattering a glowing powder. The spot patterns on its back grow larger or smaller at night depending on the number of stars in the sky.

name: Spinarak
pokedex: It sets a trap by spinning a web of thin but strong silk. Then it waits for the prey to arrive. It recognizes what kind of prey has fallen on its web by the vibration received by each on of its eight legs.

name: Ariados
pokedex: This Pokémon is silent and stealthy. It comes out at night. After attaching some silk to its prey, it sets it free. Later, it tracks the silk back to the prey and its friends. It can form big colonies in caves.

name: Crobat
pokedex: Very rare in the wild. People have called it a vampire. It sneaks up on its intended prey using wings that barely make a sound. Crobat is a surprising loyal Pokémon.

name: Chinchou
pokedex: In the dark ocean floor, it's only mean of communication is to constantly flash its lights. It is a clumsy but friendly Pokémon. Its antennae can be used to power up small electric appliances.
evolution_method: Evolves after reaching a certain level.

name: Lanturn
pokedex: It is known for its soft light glow. They are not aggressive Pokémon. If you look into the dark sea at night, you can sometimes see this Pokémon's light rising from the depths making the sea look like a starry night.

name: Pichu
pokedex: Its cheek pouches are not fully developed yet. Pichu gets startled if its cheeks release electricity jolts. It needs a friendly environment to grow happy. It can be quite a rascal though.

name: Cleffa
pokedex: An extremely elusive Pokémon. A few have appeared when the night skies are filled with shooting stars - but they always disappear at dawn. Friendship and love allow it to go into the next evolutionary stage.

name: Igglybuff
pokedex: It has a very light body that makes it float and bounce. If you are not careful, it can bounce away without control. After being bottlefed, it will not bounce but wiggle around. It gets cranky if it doesn't take a nap.

name: Togepi
pokedex: This Pokémon stores all the kindness and good feelings inside of its shell and shares them with others, when the shell is full it becomes so happy that it finally evolves. It is said that it'll bring good fortune to its trainer.

name: Togetic
pokedex: Although there have been very few sightings of the Pokémon in the wild, it is known to appear before kind hearted people and grant them happiness. It is very energetic and friendly.

name: Natu
pokedex: It lives close to the deserts. Its wings are not fully developed so it hops to trees and cactus to peck something to eat. If you find one it will hold your stare, if you get closer it might disappear in an instant.
evolution_method: Evolves after making an eerie prophecy.

name: Xatu
pokedex: Xatu is known to stand motionless while staring at the sun all day long. Some people revere it as a mystical Pokémon out of their belief that Xatus have the power to see into the future.

name: Mareep
pokedex: Its fluffy coat of wool builds a static charge, the more static electricity, the more brightly the bobble at the end of its tail glows. Farmers harvest their wool in the summer, but it grows back quickly.

name: Flaaffy
pokedex: Its wool quality changes so that it can generate a higher amount of static electricity with a smaller amount of wool. The bare and slick parts of its hide are shielded with small electric impulses.

name: Ampharos
pokedex: It's not common to see it in the wild. The tip of its tail shines brightly and in the old days, people sent light signals with the help of this Pokémon. It has a good disposition towards people in general.

name: Bellossom
pokedex: They are plentiful in tropical areas. The beauty of the flowers on its head depends on how stinky it was as a Gloom. Lots of sunshine will the the skirt leaves swirl in a beautiful and rhythmic dance.

name: Marill
pokedex: Marill's tail acts like a buoy. Seeing its tail bobbing on the water's surface is a sure indication that this Pokémon is diving to feed on algae and aquatic plants. This Pokémon is curious towards humans.
evolution_method: Evolves after reaching a certain level.

name: Azumarill
pokedex: It stays in water virtually all day long. Its blue fur makes it difficult to spot when submerged. Azumarill uses its sensitive ears to locate prey, even when underwater. They are not aggressive and even get close to humans.

name: Sudowoodo
pokedex: Sudowoodo camouflages itself as a tree to avoid being attacked by enemies. However, because its arms remain green throughout the year, this Pokémon is easy to identify in winter. It's a little wary of humans.

name: Politoed
pokedex: It lives with Poliwags and Poliwhirls near ponds and lakes, but there's rarely more than one. Politoed is the leader and acts as the king of the group. It is an easy-going but proud Pokémon.

name: Hoppip
pokedex: This Pokémon drifts away by floating in the wind. Even the weakest current can lift them up. By the end of the winter you can see them flying above cities and fields. This means that spring is coming soon.

name: Skiploom
pokedex: It blooms when the weather is warm. If the weather gets cold, the bloom will close and it wall stop floating. This is not an aggressive Pokémon, but it can cause allergies if it floats directly above you.

name: Jumpluff
pokedex: It floats with the wind and spreads its cotton-like spores all over the world in order to make offspring. It is always looking for warm places. If it gets caught by a cold front it will land to find shelter.

name: Aipom
pokedex: It lives at the top of tall trees in forests and jungles. It uses its tail tip as a third hand. However, because the Pokémon uses its tail so much, its real hands become rather clumsy. It is very playful.

name: Sunkern
pokedex: They suddenly appear after a cold winter. They survive by drinking only dewdrops from under the leaves of plants. It tries not to move a lot since lots of bird Pokémon prey on them.

name: Sunflora
pokedex: Sunflora live in flower patches. They convert solar energy into nutrition and are highly active in the warm daytime, but suddenly stop moving as soon as the sun sets, closing their petals to cover their face.

name: Yanma
pokedex: It lives near water sources. Its eyes can see 360 degrees without even moving. Yanma is a great flyer, capable of making sudden stops and turning midair to quickly chase down targeted prey.
evolution_method: Evolves after contact with Primal Forces

name: Wooper
pokedex: Inhabits cold water sources and only comes out during the evening when the land has cooled to find something to eat. Under this ideal environment, it has rarely been seen at its evolved stage.
evolution_method: Evolves after a sudden climate change.

name: Quagsire
pokedex: You'll find its home at the bottom of the river. It hunts by leaving its mouth wide open in the water and waiting for prey to get in. Because it doesn't move a lot, it does not get very hungry.

name: Espeon
pokedex: Espeon is extremely loyal to the trainer it considers worthy. It is said to have developed precognitive powers to protect its trainer from harm. The orb on its forehead glows whenever it uses psychic energy.

name: Umbreon
pokedex: Umbreon evolved from exposure to the moon's energy pulses. It lurks in darkness and waits for its foes to move. The rings on its body glow when it leaps to attack. Its fur is drenched with a mild poison.

name: Murkrow
pokedex: Murkrows are feared and loathed as the alleged bearers of ill fortune. This Pokémon will steal anything that sparkles. They ar infamous for luring people into winding mountain passes where they become lost.

name: Slowking
pokedex: Slowking is extremely rare. The Shellder on its head injects a poison that made it super intelligent. It takes a lot of interest in learning about Pokémon lore and legends. If Shellder is knocked out, it will forget everything.

name: Misdreavus
pokedex: Misdreavus frightens people with a creepy, sobbing cry. It uses the red spheres on its neck to absorb fear as nutrition. It takes a wicked pleasure in startling and scaring people.

name: Unown
pokedex: There are depictions of it in ancient ruins. When Unknowns are gathered, it is said that a strange power capable of anything emerges. They are all shaped like letters, each one of them with a unique power.

name: Wobbuffet
pokedex: Wobbuffet looks somewhat deflated until it senses an aggressor, then it inflates. It will do nothing beside endure and counter attacks. It always keeps its black tail hidden, the reasons are still a mystery.

name: Girafarig
pokedex: Its tail is a head of its own, it bites if anything comes close and never rests. Some say that the sum of its two heads grant it psychic powers. Even if that's true, the tail isn't very bright, but it is quite vicious.

name: Pineco
pokedex: Pineco looks like a regular pine cone. It adds layers of tree bark as a shield from harm. It waits for bugs to eat while hanging from branches. If anyone shakes its tree it falls down and explodes. Be very careful.

name: Forretress
pokedex: It can be found completely rooted to huge tree trunks. It protects itself and its tree by scattering spiked pieces from its shell and turning its home into a fortress that won't go down without a fight.

name: Dunsparce
pokedex: If seen, Dunsparce is quick to escape by boring into the ground with its drill tail. It can float slightly with its wings. It is almost blind, but finds its way in the huge underground mazes where it lives.

name: Gligar
pokedex: It hangs from cliffs waiting for its prey. It flies straight at the target's face, grapples the victim with its pincers and claws hind legs, lastly it injects poison with its tail. Gligar can glide without making any noise.
evolution_method: Evolves by using a Razor Fang for a long time.

name: Steelix
pokedex: When an Onix lives underground for 100 years, its body accumulates iron and becomes hard as steel. As it travels deeper into iron deposits the high heat and pressure temper its shell. It can see in the darkness.

name: Snubbull
pokedex: It may look frightening, but it is a loving and caring creature, active and playful. Snubbulls are easily scared. When threatened by bigger foes, they run away or make scary faces, that makes them sad though.
evolution_method: Evolves by learning to be brave

name: Granbull
pokedex: Granbull is usually a timid creature that is easily spooked. Its fangs are extremely powerful and scary, so no one dares to mess with it or its loved ones. It will use its giant fangs to attack if it needs to.

name: Qwilfish
pokedex: It swallows water to inflate its body to appear bigger than its foes. Qwilfish must swallow 2 gallons of water to be able to shoot its stings. The poison produced by Qwilfish is known to cause fainting.

name: Scizor
pokedex: Its pincers appear to be two more heads and its wings are not for flying, but to regulate its body temperature. Scizors body can shrug off most attacks and its pincers can crush almost any object

name: Shuckle
pokedex: Shuckle is a very peaceful and patient gooey worm. The fluids secreted by its toes can make holes in rocks. It hides inside those hollow stones and wears them as a shell. It is known for storing berries inside.

name: Heracross
pokedex: A docile creature that loves honey. They batter down trees with their powerful horn and chase off anyone who gets close to their prized honey. Not many Pokémon dare to mess with it in the wild.

name: Sneasel
pokedex: It drives weaker Pokémon from their homes and eats their eggs. They are vicious and cunning. They wait for prey hidden in the darkness and enjoy slashing their foes until they get tired or the foe stops moving.
evolution_method: Evolves by using a Razor Claw for a long time.

name: Teddiursa
pokedex: If they find honey, their crescent moon mark glows. They hoard food for winter and concoct their own honey by mixing fruits and pollen collected by Beedrills. They live in forests with their mothers.
evolution_method: Evolves after reaching a certain level.

name: Ursaring
pokedex: They are incredibly strong, great climbers, and posses an amazing sense of smell. They snap trees and feed on their fruit as the eat quite a lot. A forest full of scratched trees marks the territory of Ursarings.

name: Slugma
pokedex: They are extremely common in volcanic areas where they group together. They are made of molten magma instead of blood and flesh. Slugmas replenish parts of their body by absorbing molten rocks.
evolution_method: Evolves after 1000 years of living near volcanoes.

name: Magcargo
pokedex: Their shell is molten rock that cooled off and hardened. It may appear solid, but it may burst into flames with a single touch. Water vaporizes on contact and rain turns into a cloud of steam.

name: Swinub
pokedex: They rub their snout on the icy ground to find food and hot springs. Their favorite food is a mushroom that grows under frozen grass. They recognize everything by smell as their eyes can't see very well.
evolution_method: Evolves after reaching a certain level

name: Piloswine
pokedex: Their long hair obscures their sight, but they're sensitive to sound and smells. Piloswine has rugged hooves which prevent it from slipping on icy terrains. Amazingly, their tusks are made of solid ice.
evolution_method: Evolves after contact with Primal Forces

name: Corsola
pokedex: People and Pokémon build their communities on top of the reefs of these creatures which shine with seven colors in sunlight. Their corals have healing qualities and their presence wards against disasters.

name: Remoraid
pokedex: Remoraid has a remarkable aim with its water gun. This ability is used to hunt down flying enemies above the sea. They can be seen clinging onto Mantine to travel faster.
evolution_method: Evolves after a big change of environment.

name: Octillery
pokedex: Octillery sprays ink, traps their foes with its tentacles then hits them with its rock-hard head. If the enemy is to strong, they escape. They can be found inside rocky holes deep in the sea floor.

name: Delibird
pokedex: Delibird is always carrying food for its chicks and people in need. They are related to the image of Santa Claus since they always carry presents for their kids in their bag-like tail.

name: Mantine
pokedex: Mantine swims underwater and over the waves, gliding 300 ft in the air. They are intelligent and docile, traveling elegantly in groups. Remoraids can be seen hanging from their fins from time to time.

name: Skarmory
pokedex: Their wings are hollow and light. They nest inside bramble bushes, growing harder from scratches made by thorns. Their wings were used as swords and knives in old times. Beware of their sharp beak.

name: Houndour
pokedex: They hunt in coordinated packs to corner their prey. They howl at dawn to announce that this is their territory and bark to communicate tactics. Their teamwork is very efficient and they rarely welcome strangers.
evolution_method: Evolves after reaching a certain level.

name: Houndoom
pokedex: It is said the pain from its flames never goes away. Long ago, their howl was thought to be the call of the grim reaper. Pokémon and people who hear it, will always shiver in fear. They are pack leaders, not followers.

name: Kingdra
pokedex: Kingdra sleeps on the seafloor where it is otherwise devoid of life. When a storm arrives, it is said to awaken and wander about in search of prey. They are known for creating twisters in the sea.
evolution_method: Evolved when holding a dragon fang.

name: Phanpy
pokedex: They are affectionate and playful, but their snout is so strong that they may hurt others while playing. They dig pits at the edge of rivers and mark them so everyone knows that place is taken.
evolution_method: Evolves after reaching a certain level.

name: Donphan
pokedex: Strong enough to knock down a house. They like to attack by rolling as a ball at high speed, however, once they start rolling they have a hard time stopping. Some may keep their loving Phanpy nature.

name: Porygon 2
pokedex: This man made Pokémon is an upgraded version of Porygon. Used for space exploration and planetary development, boasting the power of science. Its AI software allows it to learn on its own.

name: Stantler
pokedex: Their antlers create a distortion in space that causes confusion. They were hunted for their magnificent antlers that were traded at high prices. This drove Stantlers close to extinction.

name: Smeargle
pokedex: A special ink oozes from its tail to mark its territory. They are skilled artists, known for painting action scenes from great battles. If they study their painting for a long time, they learn those moves.

name: Tyrogue
pokedex: Tyrogue is an energetic competitive and fearless Pokémon that's always looking to get stronger, fighting any enemies even if it loses. They attack anyone, anyday, anytime, everyday, without warning.
evolution_method: Evolves by maxing out certain attributes.

name: Hitmontop
pokedex: They launch high speed kicks while spinning so fast that they get drilled into the ground. They move quicker by spinning than they do walking. They are very smart and like to perform dance-like kicks.
evolution_method: Evolved by maxing out Strength and Vitality

name: Smoochum
pokedex: They examine their surroundings with their lips. They love to smooch, but Pokémon dislike their kisses. Smoochums are always running excitedly, but they are clumsy and end up stumbling and crying.
evolution_method: Evolves after reaching a certain level

name: Elekid
pokedex: They can be found following thunderstorms. Elekids rotate their arms constantly to charge electricity. Beware: there is an electric current between their horns that may zap you if you touch them.
evolution_method: Evolves after reaching a certain level

name: Magby
pokedex: They inhale embers from their mouth and nostrils. Their body temperature is so hot, they may ignite anything they touch and even the floor they walk on. Magby can be found in volcanoes.
evolution_method: Evolves after reaching a certain level

name: Miltank
pokedex: A Miltank milk is full of nutrients that may heal the sick and the injured, and they can produce up to 5 gallons a day. Healing serious injuries may require a lot of milk.

name: Blissey
pokedex: Whoever takes a bite on a Blissey's egg becomes loving and caring to everyone. They are compassionate, healing anyone who's injured. Their presence makes everyone smile. An intelligent and empathic Pokémon.

name: Raikou
pokedex: Johto legends tell about a Pokémon born from lightning, with barks like crashing thunder, soaring the lands, sending resounding shockwaves as it walks.

name: Entei
pokedex: Johto legends tell about a Pokémon so powerful its bark makes volcanoes erupt, traveling the lands cloaked in a cloud of volcanic smoke.

name: Suicune
pokedex: Johto legends tell about a Pokémon that carries the north winds, sailing above the clouds as the aurora purifying water fountains, pools and rivers.

name: Larvitar
pokedex: Born deep underground, they don't emerge until they've eaten a whole mountain of soil. Only the strongest and more ferocious ever come out to roam about. They hate being disturbed.
evolution_method: Evolves after reaching a certain level.

name: Pupitar
pokedex: Even in their shell, they are fast, aggressive, and extremely destructive. They never stay still. This pupa propels itself using a jet of pressurized gas. It is bad tempered and very aggressive.

name: Tyranitar
pokedex: Its body is hardly damaged by any attack, so it's always eager to fight. They are extremely strong, their rage can change landscapes. Tyranitars are insolents, rebels, and they care about no one.

name: Lugia
pokedex: Known as the Guardian of the Sea. It used to live in the Brass Tower, where Pokémon awoke. Lugia's Myth is linked to the idea that those whose death was pure will be reborn in the sea.

name: Ho-oh
pokedex: Ho-oh inhabited the Bell Tower, where Pokémon were said to rest. Ho-oh's Myth talks about a creature that brought eternal rest for those whose time was right, and also gave back life if death was premature.

name: Celebi
pokedex: Guardian of the Forest. Celebi is said to be able to travel through time, amending mistakes from people who hurt the land, and crafting a bright future for those who live nearby.

name: Treecko
pokedex: They climb trees with their spiked feet. They remain cool under stress, calm under pressure, and collected when endangered. They are found protecting the trees ferociously.
evolution_method: Evolves after reaching a certain level.

name: Grovyle
pokedex: Their leaves provide camouflage in the jungles. They appear to fly from tree to tree, jumping huge lengths with amazing speed. It's almost impossible to catch them once they start running away.
evolution_method: Evolves after reaching a certain level.

name: Sceptile
pokedex: They raise trees with love and care and protect the jungles with their lives. Their tails can restore a plant's beauty. Sceptiles power is truly unmatched in their habitats. They are very proud though.

name: Torchic
pokedex: They walk clumsily, but follow their trainers wherever they go. Torchics have a flame sac in their belly - burning all the time. If you hug them, they feel warm, if you squeeze them they may spit fire.
evolution_method: Evolves after reaching a certain level.

name: Combusken
pokedex: They love to run and kick. They have an offensive instinct to keep attacking no matter what. They squawk loudly every morning when they start to train.
evolution_method: Evolves after reaching a certain level.

name: Blaziken
pokedex: They can jump incredible heights. As they grow older, their feathers combust as new feathers grow back. They are courageous fighters and expert martial artists. Their wrists light in flames when it's about to attack.

name: Mudkip
pokedex: The fin on its head is a radar to sense movement underwater. They bury themselves under the mud at the water's edge and at the bottom of rivers. They never back away even if their foe is bigger.
evolution_method: Evolves after reaching a certain level.

name: Marshtomp
pokedex: A sticky film allows them to live out of the water. They are seen playing in the mud at beaches to rehydrate their dry bodies. They are slow runners and swimmers, but they can be fast sliding through the mud.
evolution_method: Evolves after reaching a certain level.

name: Swampert
pokedex: They have an incredible sight that allows them to see in muddy water. They nest in beaches, and shield their young with their strong arms. When a storm is coming, Swampert build a fort with big rocks.

name: Poochyena
pokedex: Poochyena will bite anything that moves. They will chase people and other Pokémon for dozens of miles without losing track. This Pokémon is persistent and tenacious. In the wild, they form small hunting packs.

name: Mightyena
pokedex: They attack savagely, travel in packs, and hunt in groups. They will only obey trainers that show superior skills, which they recognize as the alpha leader. They are extremely obedient once they find a master.

name: Zigzagoon
pokedex: They are extremely curious and want to know about everything. Due to their innate curiosity, they usually find hidden objects. Sometimes they play dead to avoid being attacked.
evolution_method: Evolves after reaching a certain level.

name: Linoone
pokedex: Linoones are always running at full speed, but they can only do so in straight lines. They find it very difficult to deal with any curved road. They excel at hunting but tend to eat a lot to cover from their tiring runs.

name: Wurmple
pokedex: It uses its spikes on its rear to peel the trees and feed on their sap. Their feet have suction pads to climb easily. Wurmples are plentiful and live in forests, but they are often attacked by bird Pokémon.

name: Silcoon
pokedex: They tether themselves to tree branches while they wait to evolve. Sometimes they peek from a small hole in the cocoon. Silcoon feed only on raindrops. If Wurmple lived among flowers, it evolves into Silcoon.

name: Beautifly
pokedex: They can't resist the pollen of flowers, if you leave one in the window, a Beautifly is sure to come. Despite their appearance, they are aggressive. They drain living creatures of their fluids just as they do with flowers.

name: Cascoon
pokedex: They hide between huge leaves and gaps between branches. If they were to move, their evolution would be weaker. Due to this, Cascoon will remain motionless. If Wurmple lived in a dark place, it evolves to Cascoon.

name: Dustox
pokedex: They travel in big groups during the night, attracted to bright lights and big cities. Their flight releases a poisonous shining dust that causes mayhem in towns. For this reason people dislike them.

name: Lotad
pokedex: They live in ponds and lakes, floating atop the water. The big leaf on their head is known to act as a ferry for smaller Pokémon. The leaf is delicate and needs constant watering or else Lotad will grow sick.
evolution_method: Evolves after reaching a certain size.

name: Lombre
pokedex: This nocturnal Pokémon has a mischievous and impish personality. While playing pranks on people, Lombres are commonly mistaken for human children. It enjoys to startle unaware swimmers.

name: Ludicolo
pokedex: Ludicolo starts dancing at the sound of music. Pokémon and people will dance as well. They are said to appear when children sing. They love festive places and parties.

name: Seedot
pokedex: They attach to tree branches to suck moisture from them. While immobile, they young are identical to real acorns. They enjoy scaring other Pokémon, especially Pidgey. If they fall, they are at risk of being eaten.
evolution_method: Evolves after reaching a certain size.

name: Nuzleaf
pokedex: They live inside holes on big trees. Their leaves are played like flutes to strike fear and discomfort in lost people's hearts. They like to go out and startle people. Their noses are really sensitive and frail.

name: Shiftry
pokedex: Feared as protectors of the forest. They are said to live atop towering trees dating back thousands of years, creating terrible wind storms. It is said they can read people's minds to prey on their fears.

name: Taillow
pokedex: They are brave and noble, facing bigger foes whoever they might be. However, being the immature form of the evolution line, it usually feels lonely and cries at night. They can be seen migrating south in the winter.
evolution_method: Evolves after reaching a certain level.

name: Swellow
pokedex: They are vain Pokémon, acting with grace and elegance. Swellows are seen circling the skies looking for prey. They can be incredibly fast. If two Swellow's meet, they will clean each other's wings as a sign of peace.

name: Wingull
pokedex: They carry prey and precious items in their beaks, hiding them in strange locations. They nest in sheer cliffs at the sea's edge. They often harass fishing boats to steal an easy meal for themselves.
evolution_method: Evolves after reaching a certain level.

name: Pelipper
pokedex: Pelipper has been seen carrying eggs and other Pokémon inside its massive bill, protecting them from predators and storms, transporting the young through the great seas.

name: Ralts
pokedex: They sense the emotions of people and Pokémon, usually sharing the mood of anyone nearby. They show if they feel joy and cheer, but hide if they sense hostility. They dislike fighting and negativity.
evolution_method: Evolves after a powerful and happy moment.

name: Kirlia
pokedex: When they use their powers, their surroundings are distorted with mirages and ilusor sceneries from the future and the past. Kirlia like to dance and dislike to be bossed around.
evolution_method: Evolves differently for males and females.

name: Gardevoir
pokedex: If they sense danger, Gardevoir unleash a wave of psychic energy. They can distort this dimension, defying the laws of matter and physics. They risk their lives to protect their fellows.
evolution_method: Female Kirlia evolved with a Shiny Stone.

name: Surskit
pokedex: Surskit secretes oil from its feet to skate on water. It may be found on ponds, lakes, and puddles in towns. The tip of its head produces a delicious sugary syrup often used in desserts and sweets.

name: Masquerain
pokedex: Their antennas look like terrifying eyes. Masquerain can fly in any direction like a helicopter, but their wings are soft and fragile, so they can't fly when it's raining. They cling to trees at night to sleep.

name: Shroomish
pokedex: They live in damp soil in forests surrounded by moss. They suddenly release toxic spores and wilt plants. These spores cause serious pain if inhaled. They grow with moisture and heat.
evolution_method: Evolves after reaching a certain size.

name: Breloom
pokedex: Their flexible arms and quick footwork can put good fighters to shame. The seeds on their tail and the cap on their head release poison spores. They love humid and hot climates.

name: Slakoth
pokedex: They laze around 20 hours a day, barely eating. Slakoths remain motionless no matter what. It's rare to see this Pokémon doing something, most of them never even bother to evolve.
evolution_method: Evolves after being full of energy.

name: Vigoroth
pokedex: They are always agitated, anxious, excited, or upset, rampaging over anything. They can't be still and they can't sleep. They get angry if they get bored and violent if there is no activity for them.
evolution_method: Evolves if they are encouraged to be lazy.

name: Slaking
pokedex: They spend all day sleeping and eating grass that grows within their reach. Sometimes they live beneath trees, waiting for fruits to fall. They dislike intruders on their territory, but rarely do anything about them.

name: Nincada
pokedex: They live underground for decades, absorbing nutrients from roots and waiting for evolution. Nincadas are nearly blind and cannot stand bright lights. They only come out to make a cocoon to evolve.

name: Ninjask
pokedex: Due to their speed and stealthiness this Pokémon was believed to be invisible. They refuse to obey people and cry continuously if forced. People burn their cocoons as they are said to be cursed.

name: Shedinja
pokedex: Genderless. On extremely rare occasion: when Nincada evolves, the empty cocoon comes to life. They don't move, they only float unnaturally around. It is said that it will steal the soul of anyone looking directly at them.

name: Whismur
pokedex: Their timid voice is barely audible, however, if it senses danger, they start crying loud enough to deafen anyone nearby. Their own noise scares them even more, so they cry harder until their ear covers shut.
evolution_method: Evolves after reaching a certain level.

name: Loudred
pokedex: Their ears work as loudspeakers capable of breaking glass or even blowing apart a wooden house. When it finishes shouting, even they are deafened for a while. They have noisy competitions in their packs.
evolution_method: Evolves after reaching a certain level.

name: Exploud
pokedex: It is said that some tremors are caused by the roars of this Pokémon. They communicate with soft noises, raising their voice only in battle. They can emit many different kinds of sounds.

name: Makuhita
pokedex: A tenacious Pokémon that will get back up no matter how many times he gets knocked down. They have a tireless spirit, and never give up hope. Makuhita put all their hearts into everything they do.
evolution_method: Evolves after getting knocked down many times.

name: Hariyama
pokedex: They may appear fat, but they are pure muscle. Haryama have the habit of challenging big looking creatures to test their strength, sometimes mistaking cars and machines for real Pokémon.

name: Azurill
pokedex: They use their tail as a lasso. When they throw their ball, Azurill gets dragged along with it. They are commonly seen bouncing and playing with other Pokémon on the beach. They love fruit pops.

name: Nosepass
pokedex: Their magnetic noses always point to the north. They were thought to be immobile, but it was recently revealed that they actually move 3/8 of an inch every year. They get a little crazy when magnets are close.
evolution_method: Evolves when exposed to strong natural magnetic fields.

name: Skitty
pokedex: They are fascinated by moving objects, even chasing their own tail without hesitation. They are cute by nature, and popular pets, but it's hard to earn their trust in the wild. They are quite affectionate.

name: Delcatty
pokedex: They like to live without restrictions, spending their time eating and sleeping whenever they feel like it. Popular among females. Delcatty love clean places, good food, and grooming themselves.

name: Sableye
pokedex: Feared for stealing the souls of men with their sinister eyes glowing in the dark. They lurk deep inside caves, eating rocks, gemstones and crystals. Luckily, Sableye are rarely seen. They love jewels and treasure.

name: Mawile
pokedex: They appear to be cute and docile, luring their prey and lowering their guards, then, Mawile chomps the prey with huge steel jaws. They are very rare though. Only a few have been seen in Hoenn Victory Road.

name: Aron
pokedex: They can be seen feeding on iron ore in the mountains or causing trouble by eating rails, bridges and vehicles. When they evolve Aron shed their steel armor and develop a stronger one.
evolution_method: Evolves after reaching a certain level.

name: Lairon
pokedex: Their armor gets stronger by eating iron ore and drinking mineral spring water, usually nesting close to ponds. Lairon often attack human miners. They are territorial creatures, incredibly stubborn and resilient.

name: Aggron
pokedex: Aggron claims ownership of entire mountains, mercilessly beating up anything that crosses its path. Aggron are violent and patrol their territory at all times, but also plant trees, stop fires, and protect nature.

name: Meditite
pokedex: Deep in the mountains they train their mind to increase their spiritual power, however they lack focus and get distracted easily. As part of their training, Meditite barely eat.
evolution_method: Evolves by learning to focus its powers.

name: Medicham
pokedex: They are thought to possess a sixth sense. Some of them can hide their presence by lowering their ki. Medicham fight with expert yoga moves, foretelling their foes attacks and sensing their thoughts.

name: Electrike
pokedex: Their fur stores electricity, leaving a trail of sparks as they run. By stimulating their legs with voltage, Electrike's speed and power is greatly increased. They are not very common.
