evolution_method: Evolves after reaching a certain level.

name: Manectric
pokedex: Their manes are constantly releasing dangerous sparks that often end up in forest fires. When they get in battle, thunderclouds show up with them. They are extremely rare to see in the wild.

name: Plusle
pokedex: They are often seen cheerleading their friends. When someone they like does a great job, they shower the field with sparks, but when they lose, Plusle cries loudly. This Pokémon drains power from telephone poles.

name: Minun
pokedex: They will cheer their friends with their lives and will keep on cheering to their last breath. If a partner is in trouble, this Pokémon will create a curtain of sparks on its friend's side to boost its spirits.

name: Volbeat
pokedex: The male of its species. Their tail shines bright during the night, drawing geometric shapes in the sky. Volbeat live in swarms around clean ponds. They are attracted to Illumise sweet aroma.

name: Illumise
pokedex: They attract swarms of Volbeat with their sweet fragrance and organize the swarm into drawing geometric shapes made of light. Illumise gain rank in their group if they make an amazing performance.

name: Roselia
pokedex: They live among rose bushes, shooting sharp poisonous thorns to anyone who tries to steal one of their flowers. Their aroma brings serenity. They need clean water to grow beautiful.

name: Gulpin
pokedex: Gulpin's body is a huge stomach capable of swallowing anything their size. Their fluids can digest even metal. This Pokémon releases hideous and vile gases while it is digesting.
evolution_method: Evolves after reaching a certain size.

name: Swalot
pokedex: Swalot spurt toxic fluids from their pores, and once the prey is weak, it gets swallowed whole since they have no teeth. They may eat anything up to the size of a car's tire. Do not get too close to them.

name: Carvanha
pokedex: Anything near a Carvanha school will be swarmed, attacked and tore to bits. However, they are very timid when they are on their own. They live in rivers in the jungle and dislike salt water.
evolution_method: Evolves by living in salt water for too long.

name: Sharpedo
pokedex: Known as the "Bully of the Sea", widely feared for its cruelty, malice, and gangster attitude. They hurt Pokémon for fun and sink boats for sport. Sharpedos are among the fastest swimmers.

name: Wailmer
pokedex: Wailmer has a playful nature. They can store water inside their body to inflate like a ball and bounce, then startle people by snorting the water from their nostrils. This PokÃ©mon needs lots of food everyday.

name: Wailord
pokedex: The largest Pokémon not to date. Wailords weight is really light, so they can dive almost 10,000 feet with one breath. They live in open ocean herding fish to swallow in one gulp. They are used to freedom.

name: Numel
pokedex: An incredibly dim-witted Pokémon. They don't notice being hit. If they get hungry they faint. Numel's body is a cauldron of boiling magma. On rainy days, the magma cools and its speed is lowered.
evolution_method: Evolves after reaching a certain level.

name: Camerupt
pokedex: Sometimes the humps on their back make an eruption when they get really angry, otherwise they'd only erupt once every 10 years. Camerupts live inside craters of volcanoes. They are indifferent to humans.

name: Torkoal
pokedex: They constantly search for coal to add to their shell, digging mountains tirelessly because it is the source of their power. If they run out of coal, they grow weak. They are commonly found in abandoned coal mines.

name: Spoink
pokedex: They are always bouncing with their tail. If they ever stop, their heart wouldn't beat anymore. Spoink balance a pearl from Clamperl on their head. If it's lost, they won't be able to control their psychic powers.
evolution_method: Evolves by learning to control its powers.

name: Grumpig
pokedex: Grumpig control their foes with their psychic powers amplified by the pearls on their head and a hypnotic dance. However, when they use their powers, they have a difficult time breathing.

name: Spinda
pokedex: Spinda move while stumbling in dizziness. This teeter dance causes a severe confusion on whoever is looking. They are shy towards humans, but sometimes they appear in towns looking really disoriented.

name: Trapinch
pokedex: Their nest is like a bowl pit dug in the sand. Trapinches wait for prey to tumble down their pit, later to be crushed between this Pokémon's jaws. Beware of them as their bite can cause serious damage.
evolution_method: Evolves after reaching a certain level

name: Vibrava
pokedex: This Pokémon's vibrations can cause severe headaches or even fainting. If their prey faints, they proceed to melt them with acid. Vibrava's wings are still growing, making it a clumsy flier with low endurance.

name: Flygon
pokedex: Known as the "Elemental Spirit of the Desert". Their wings create a cloud of dust that surrounds this Pokémon while flying, while their flapping produces a sound that resembles a woman singing.

name: Cacnea
pokedex: They release a strong and sweet aroma to attract prey, if they get closer. Cacneas shoot sharp thorns to bring them down. They resemble cactuses and hide among them.

name: Cacturne
pokedex: They only move during the night. If they spot a traveler, Cacturne will stalk them in groups, waiting for the exhausted creatures to sleep before attacking. Their insides are actually sand.

name: Swablu
pokedex: Their wings are made of cotton clouds. They are friendly creatures that love to be near humans, usually sitting on their heads as cotton hats. They travel in flocks and live near towns during the Spring.
evolution_method: Evolves after reaching a certain size.

name: Altaria
pokedex: Seen as dancing clouds in the sky, Altaria sing melodies in their sweet voices, evoking wonder, beauty, and  dreams to the listeners. They live far away from people and throw colorful fireballs at uninvited guests.

name: Zangoose
pokedex: The sole desire to battle Sevipers is embedded in their genes. They have been rivals for countless eras. Zangoose is a very agile quadrupede, standing up on two legs only when it is ready to fight.

name: Seviper
pokedex: Their hate for Zangoose has been boiling for so long it's now a basic instinct. They battle using their sword-edged poisonous tail hiding in tall grass until an unwary prey gets close enough.

name: Lunatone
pokedex: Genderless. First found where a meteorite fell. For this reason, it's believed it came from space. Its eyes fill people with dread and lure them to sleep. They become very active and extremely powerful during full moons.

name: Solrock
pokedex: Genderless. People say it came from space. They release the purest light when they get angry. Usually found absorbing solar light during the day, Solrocks can emit blinding lights and burning heat while spinning.

name: Barboach
pokedex: Their whiskers work as a super sensitive radar. They hide in the mud with only their whiskers exposed, waiting for prey to come. If the mud dries, they move back into the water.
evolution_method: Evolves after reaching a certain level.

name: Whiscash
pokedex: Dangerous and territorial, they claim entire ponds as their homes and will crush with earthquakes whoever dares to dive in. They eat anything alive in their pond or swamp. They learn to foretell real tremors.

name: Corphish
pokedex: Corphish were originally foreign Pokémon that were imported as pets. They eventually turned up in the wild and reproduced a lot. They are resilient and can live in polluted water. Beware of their pincers.
evolution_method: Evolves after reaching a certain level.

name: Crawdaunt
pokedex: Crawdaunt is extremely violent and territorial. The ponds where it lives look like desolated places due to them attacking anything that comes close. It sheds its shell once a year. This weakens it for a few days.

name: Baltoy
pokedex: Genderless. They spin on their center to move around. When a group of them gathers, they create a horrible headache-inducing noise in unison. Old paintings describe them living with people in ancient times.
evolution_method: It's not known what makes them evolve.

name: Claydol
pokedex: Genderless. It is made entirely of clay. The first one was discovered in ruins from 20,000 years ago. A strange light is said to be the source of its life and psychic abilities. Its eight eyes are always alert and always watching.

name: Lileep
pokedex: Over 100 million years ago, Lileep used to attach themselves to rocks at the bottom of the sea. A catastrophe led them all to extinction. A few fossils were found and some were revived by scientists.
evolution_method: Evolves after reaching a certain size.

name: Cradily
pokedex: Cradily moves slowly at the bottom of the sea. It uses its body as an anchor and its tentacles as arms to catch prey. Their foes are melted with a potent acid before being consumed.

name: Anorith
pokedex: This ancient Pokémon is thought to be the common ancestor of many modern Bug Pokémon. The fossils show it lived in big schools and it preferred warm waters. Anorith used their claws to catch small prey.
evolution_method: Evolves after reaching a certain level.

name: Armaldo
pokedex: When the waters receded, this Pokémon was forced to evolve and live on land. Evidence suggests that its claws could extend to reach the prey that was far away or underwater. Its tough shell made it very resilient.

name: Feebas
pokedex: This Pokémon tastes awful. It is incredibly ugly, smell, kind of dumb and a terrible fighter. To make things worse, it is actually extremely rare. For those reasons, people tend to avoid it and it's usually ignored.
evolution_method: Evolves by reaching 5 points in Beauty.

name: Milotic
pokedex: Milotic is considered to be one of the most beautiful Pokémon in existence. It has inspired music, paintings, and statues. It has the power to calm the anger and hostility of its foes.

name: Castform
pokedex: This Pokémon reacts to the weather by changing its type and looks. It can also change the weather at will. When there is a drought, farmers lure them with small hanging dolls to ask them for rain.

name: Kecleon
pokedex: They are able to change their colors to blend with their surroundings. The only part of its body that can't change is the red zigzag line on its belly. Kecleon is very sneaky, smart, and kind of insolent.

name: Shuppet
pokedex: They feed on dark emotions such as envy, jealousy, and vengefulness. If they sting you, they'll fill you with a vindictive desire. They don't have bodies under their blanket and they are looking for a body to possess.
evolution_method: Evolves when it finds a discarded doll to possess.

name: Banette
pokedex: Its body is usually a discarded doll or toy. Its spirit is made of dark feelings and is overrun by the desire of revenge towards the kid that threw away the toy. If you open its mouth, all the cursed energy will escape.

name: Duskull
pokedex: They wander at night. They can make themselves invisible and they follow travelers all night until dawn breaks. It loves the crying of little children, they can be seen scaring kids who misbehaved during the day.
evolution_method: Evolves after scaring hundreds of people.

name: Dusclops
pokedex: Its body is hollow. Some paranormal experts say there is a spectral energy ball inside them, but it is not confirmed. If it absorbs an object or a creature, there's the risk that nothing will come back out.
evolution_method: Evolves after being traded holding a certain item.

name: Tropius
pokedex: It is very common in humid and hot regions. It can grow back the fruit it has eaten. Mothers prefer Tropius fruits to feed their children as it is more nutritive and sweet. They are mellow and friendly Pokémon.

name: Chimecho
pokedex: They have seven different cries that resound with the wind. They can create ultrasonic waves when they are in danger. Using the suction cup on their head, they hang to branches on windy days.

name: Absol
pokedex: It is said that this Pokémon can live for 100 years. It has a bad reputation: whenever one is seen, a disaster is soon to follow - earthquakes, forest fires, and tidal waves. Absols lead a lonely life.

name: Wynaut
pokedex: Its face always appears to be happy, but Wynaut can be deceitful. Only through its tail that you'll know its true emotions. They live together in caves and bump into each other to gain strength.
evolution_method: Evolves after reaching a certain size.

name: Snorunt
pokedex: This friendly Pokémon lives in cold mountains and deserted snowlands. It survives by eating snow and ice. They form small groups to protect themselves from predators. If you take their hat off, they will get angry.
evolution_method: Evolves differently for males and females.

name: Glalie
pokedex: Its body is so hard it was thought to be made of rock. They can be aggressive if provoked. When they hunt, they freeze their prey solid before eating it. They can live in warm places without trouble.
evolution_method: Male Snorunt evolved by becoming unmeltable.

name: Spheal
pokedex: They live in big herds with their families. They are bad swimmers, but good floaters. To move on land, they roll like balls instead of walking. When they are happy, they clap and squeal, so they can be really noisy.
evolution_method: Evolves after reaching a certain level.

name: Sealeo
pokedex: They play with the Spheal in the herd by spinning them with their noses. When they are not in the wild, they'll spin almost any round object, even Pokeballs. Sealeo are great hunters underwater.
evolution_method: Evolves after reaching a certain level.

name: Walrein
pokedex: The leader of the herd is a powerful Walreit. They are very aggressive and will protect their herd even at the cost of their lives. Their tusks can shatter giant blocks of ice. It is relentless and unpredictable.

name: Clamperl
pokedex: It is protected by a sturdy shell which is used to catch its prey. Clamperl will produce a magnificent pearl once in a lifetime. That pearl is said to increase psychic powers and will sell for a lot of money.
evolution_method: Evolves after being traded holding a certain item.

name: Huntail
pokedex: It lives at extreme depths of the sea. Their eyes can see perfectly in complete darkness. Huntails light up their tail to attract their prey, then swallow them whole with a single bite.
evolution_method: It was holding the Fang of a Pokémon.

name: Gorebyss
pokedex: Found in the depths of the southern seas. Their body is built to withstand the sea pressure. While it appears to be beautiful and harmless, it is a cruel and deceitful creature
evolution_method: It was holding the scale of a Pokémon.

name: Relicanth
pokedex: It has remained unchanged for millions of years. Relicanth was discovered in a deep sea expedition. It feeds on plankton. Their scales are like craggy rocks. They can endure the deep pressure of the sea.

name: Luvdisc
pokedex: Luvdisc is a symbol of romance. It lives in shallow seas, swimming after couples, bringing them closer, and promising eternal love. During their spawning season, the waters around them turn pink.

name: Bagon
pokedex: Bagons dream of soaring the sky. This leads to a lot of frustration that makes them dive off cliffs in an attempt to fly. Their head is tough enough to survive the fall. They are very ill tempered and violent.

name: Shelgon
pokedex: The body is covered in a powerful armor that resembles bones. It hides in caves awaiting evolution, enduring hunger and harm while its cells prepare for its final transformation.

name: Salamence
pokedex: After a lifetime of struggling for a dream, it finally grew its wings. Salamence, however, is extremely dangerous. It scorches entire fields and mountains. It's easily angered and completely uncontrollable.

name: Beldum
pokedex: Genderless. Beldum uses magnetic pulses to float and communicate. When it finds others, they move in perfect unison. It needs to develop a new brain to evolve; two of them may merge or it could develop a new one with time.

name: Metang
pokedex: Genderless. Its two brains are joined by a magnetic nervous system. This allows Metang to use psychokinetic powers. It is able to float and move in midair at 60 mph. To further evolve, it will need more brain power.
evolution_method: Evolves by developing two more brains.

name: Metagross
pokedex: Genderless. It has four powerful brains that allow it to react at the speed of a supercomputer. It pins its prey under its massive body, then eats it using the large mouth on its stomach. A powerful and ruthless Pokémon.

name: Regirock
pokedex: It is said to be an immortal being the size of the peak of a mountain. Could he be a remnant from the most ancient times of this world?

name: Regice
pokedex: It is said to be indistinguishable from a gigantic iceberg. Its myth says its body can't be melted, even if submerged in magma. Regice could freeze the air to bring a new ice age.

name: Registeel
pokedex: Its body was indestructible. A flexible metal out of this world that can shrink, expand, and be made solid or liquid at the speed of thought. Could the myths be true?

name: Latias
pokedex: The legend tells about two Pokémon that could take human shapes, use psychic powers and become invisible. They were raised by an old couple as their own children. The little girl had a red dress.

name: Latios
pokedex: The legend tells about two Pokémon that could take human shapes, use psychic powers, and become invisible. They were raised by an old couple as their own children. The boy was the oldest and wore a blue shirt.

name: Kyogre
pokedex: Kyogre is named in mythology as the God that expanded the seas and oceans with torrential waters and huge tidal waves. He is the mortal enemy of Groudon.

name: Groudon
pokedex: Described in mythology as the God creator of lands, mountains, volcanoes, and continents. Any water or clouds evaporate in his presence. He is the mortal enemy of Kyogre.

name: Rayquaza
pokedex: The legend tells how Rayquaza lived in the outer layer of this world. It came to end the quarrel between Groudon and Kyogre. Granted the world with blue skies and left.

name: Jirachi
pokedex: It is said that every 1000 years, a shooting star appears in the sky for 7 days, granting wishes for those of pure heart. Another common saying is: "Be careful what you wish for"

name: Deoxys (Normal Forme)
pokedex: A space expedition had to be aborted due to an emergency. The astronauts told about a creature mutating and attacking them. They all gave different descriptions of the attacker.

name: Turtwig
pokedex: It makes its home close to lakes, although it is rare to find one. The shell on its back is made of hardened soil, and should be kept moist for it to stay healthy. It uses photosynthesis to get energy.
evolution_method: Evolves after reaching a certain level.

name: Grotle
pokedex: Other Pokémon harass Grotle when the bushes on its back have berries or fruit. It patiently waits for others to finish eating before moving. It loves clear water and it is good at finding cool ponds and springs.
evolution_method: Evolves after reaching a certain level.

name: Torterra
pokedex: Torterra travel in groups, mistaken as moving forests. Many Pokémon make their nest on its back and live there for their entire lives. Ancient people thought that they lived on the back of a giant torterra.

name: Chimchar
pokedex: They climb sheer cliffs to live at the top of the mountains. Small groups of them tend to visit human campings to steal food and objects. They are playful and will wreak havoc if they want to have fun.
evolution_method: Evolves after reaching a certain level.

name: Monferno
pokedex: It bounces off walls and ceilings to launch aerial attacks. They live in packs in distant mountains. The size of their flame and the blue pattern on their faces determine their rank. They are small, but very strong.
evolution_method: Evolves after reaching a certain level.

name: Infernape
pokedex: Its fire crown showcases its proud and fiery nature. Infernape won't hesitate to fight bigger foes and will take on any challenge they face. Once Infernape enters a battle, it won't back down until it wins.

name: Piplup
pokedex: Piplup are extremely proud. They won't take anything from anyone nor accept being taken care of. It lives along shores in northern countries. It is a good swimmer, but terrible at walking. It trips over often.
evolution_method: Evolves after reaching a certain level.

name: Prinplup
pokedex: Prinplup hunt in icy seas. They live solitary lives because they cannot stand company and will never form a group or team. They believe they are the most important thing in the world, it's almost irritating.
evolution_method: Evolves after reaching a certain level.

name: Empoleon
pokedex: They are regal and arrogant. Their beaks slice apart the drifting ice while swimming as fast as a jet boat. They avoid unnecessary fights, but will crush and cleave anyone that hurts or threatens its pride.

name: Starly
pokedex: They flock in dozens because they are very weak on their own. They live around mountains and fields, chasing bug Pokémon. Everyone hates their annoying and strident singing.
evolution_method: Evolves after reaching a certain level.

name: Staravia
pokedex: They lead a huge flock and fight other flocks for territory. If you leave it alone, it will start to make a horrible noise. It is a fierce but bad-mannered Pokémon. When they are too weak, they abandon their flocks.
evolution_method: Evolves after reaching a certain level.

name: Staraptor
pokedex: Staraptor is a savage creature. They will never stop attacking, even if they get injured, and will fight foes bigger than themselves. They are known to leave their flock to live on their own when they evolve.

name: Bidoof
pokedex: Steady as a mountain, Bidoof has nerves of steel so nothing can disturb its focus. It is agile, active, and a great team worker. They live in huge packs alongside rivers. The dams they build are incredibly sturdy.

name: Bibarel
pokedex: Bibarel dam streams with bark and mud. It is known as an industrious worker. Their constructions are very appreciated by people because a river dammed by Bibarel will never overflow.

name: Kricketot
pokedex: If you hear a xylophone-like sound at night it means that this Pokémon is roaming close. It communicates by making rhythmic sounds with its antennae. It is not aggressive and feeds on honey and tree sap.

name: Kricketune
pokedex: It can make all kind of sounds with its antennae, arms, and mouth. It signals emotions with different tunes, but scientists still cannot define what they mean. They imitate the songs they hear.

name: Shinx
pokedex: Its body transforms the energy of its own muscles into electricity. When in danger, their fur shines in a flash to blind their foes. They live with their parents and siblings in small prides.
evolution_method: Evolves after reaching a certain level.

name: Luxio
pokedex: Female Luxio stay with the pride but males roam in marauding groups, trying to become strong enough to make their own pride. Its claws and teeth are charged with electricity, approach with caution.
evolution_method: Evolves after reaching a certain level.

name: Luxray
pokedex: It is said that it can see through walls. This Pokémon can easily find hiding prey and locate its young. Male Luxrays can be found roaming alone, patrolling their territory. The females hunt in groups.

name: Budew
pokedex: It blossoms near clear ponds. Budew needs nurturing and care to grow healthy and beautiful, otherwise its bud will never bloom. If threatened, they will reveal their small but poisonous thorns.

name: Roserade
pokedex: Luring prey with a sweet scent, it uses the poison on its thorn-filled arm-whips to poison, bind, and finish off its prey. It has a dangerous appeal mixed with a graceful personality. It's very rare in the wild.

name: Cranidos
pokedex: It was resurrected from an iron ball-like fossil. It downs prey with headbutts, and tramples trees and walls with ease. They were plentiful 100 million years ago. You can't find one nowadays except as a fossil.
evolution_method: Evolves after reaching a certain level.

name: Rampardos
pokedex: Its skull withstands any magnitude of impact. As a result, its brain never gets the chance to grow. This may have been the cause of its extinction. It is capable of rolling a truck over with a single strike.

name: Shieldon
pokedex: It was cloned from a fossil dug out from a layer of clay. It is outstandingly armored. As a result, it can eat grass and berries without having to fight many Pokémon who would dare prey on it.
evolution_method: Evolves after reaching a certain level.

name: Bastiodon
pokedex: They lived in herds, millions of years ago. They would line together to shield their young. Despite its rough and scary exterior, this Pokémon is calm, gentle natured and a strict herbivore.

name: Burmy
pokedex: This Pokémon has adapted to live in the forests, deserts, and the city. It makes a cloak with the materials close to it to protect itself from the weather. Males evolve into a Mothim and Females into a Wormadam.
evolution_method: Evolves differently for males and females.

name: Wormadam (Plant)
pokedex: When Burmy evolved, its grass cloak became a part of its body, for this reason there are many variations in its body and type. It is a calm Pokémon that loves flowers. This Pokémon is female only.
evolution_method: Final Form. Female Burmy. Evolved after reaching maturity.

name: Wormadam (Sandy)
pokedex: When Burmy evolved, its Sand cloak became a part of its body, for this reason there are many variations in its body and type. It is a calm Pokémon that loves flowers. This Pokémon is female only.
evolution_method: Final Form. Female Burmy. Evolved after reaching maturity.

name: Wormadam (Trash)
pokedex: When Burmy evolved, its trash cloak became a part of its body, for this reason there are many variations in its body and type. It is a calm Pokémon that loves flowers. This Pokémon is female only.
evolution_method: Final Form. Female Burmy. Evolved after reaching maturity.

name: Mothim
pokedex: It flies near the mountains in search of honey. It is an opportunist and won't gather any honey by itself. Instead, Mothim steals from Combee hives and other Pokémon. This Pokémon is male only.
evolution_method: Final Form. Male Burmy. Evolved after reaching maturity.

name: Combee
pokedex: It forms hives around trees. It flies all day sipping the nectar from flowers to make honey. It is usually born a male, if a female is born, it will grow into a Vespiquen and start its own Hive.

name: Vespiquen
pokedex: This Pokémon is female only. It raises grubs in holes in its body and secretes pheromones to control Combee to fight and gather honey for her. It is a royal Pokémon that won't take orders from anyone.

name: Pachirisu
pokedex: It lives on top of the trees, gathering food for the cold winter months. It keeps warm by making fur balls charged with static electricity. Like other electric rodents, it stores electricity in its cheek pouches.

name: Buizel
pokedex: It is usually seen close to streams and rivers. Buizel swims by rotating its two tails like a screw, the sack around its neck swells to help it float or deflates to dive underwater and catch prey.
evolution_method: Evolves after reaching a certain level.

name: Floatzel
pokedex: It floats using its well-developed sack. They roam close to fishing spots to steal an easy meal. People allow them to hang around their boats because they help whenever a person falls into the water.

name: Cherubi
pokedex: It hides in bushes while absorbing the sunlight. Their small heads store the energy needed for evolution, but this small head is frequently eaten by other Pokémon and people so it's hard for them to evolve.

name: Cherrim
pokedex: Cherrims bloom during times of strong sunlight, their petals open fully and radiantly. If the sun is not visible it will remain as a closed bud, barely moving, trying to preserve its energy.

name: Shellos
pokedex: Its shape and coloration change depending on its habitat of salt or sweet water. Their body is very soft and squishy, but they can stretch to long lengths. It releases a purple liquid from its body if threatened.
evolution_method: Evolves after reaching a certain level.

name: Gastrodon
pokedex: It has a pliable body without any bones. If any part of its body is torn off, it will grow back in minutes. There is evidence that in prehistoric times it had a hard shell on its back for protection.

name: Ambipom
pokedex: They live in large colonies on the tallest trees, linking their tails to show friendship among herd mates. It loves fresh fruit. Ambipom uses its two tails better than its own arms to swing around.

name: Drifloon
pokedex: A Pokémon formed by the spirits of lost people and Pokémon. Children who mistake it for a real balloon often end up missing. Because it floats aimlessly, an old folktale calls it the "Signpost for Wandering Spirits."
evolution_method: Evolves by filling up with lost spirits

name: Drifblim
pokedex: They float in groups in the evenings, sometimes carrying people or Pokémon. If you notice them, they suddenly vanish. No one knows where they go at night, and those who follow them never return.

name: Buneary
pokedex: Lives in forest, grasslands, and even snowy mountains. It forms burrows and uses its soft fur to make nests and keep warm. You can see how it feels by the position of its ears. They are easily scared by humans.

name: Lopunny
pokedex: Lopunny is extremely cautious. It quickly bounds off when it senses danger. If they are touched roughly, they throw kicks and jump away. Keep the fur it sheds as it's highly valued to make quality yarn.

name: Mismagius
pokedex: Extremely rare. Their cries sound like incantations, hearing them gives you bad headaches and hallucinations. It is said that some Mismagius are benevolent and have granted good fortune to people they like.

name: Honchkrow
pokedex: It lets out a deep cry to summon Murkrows, they bring food and shiny objects to Honchkrow. It is, however, a tyrant to the Murkrow. It only goes out at night to carry out evil deeds.

name: Glameow
pokedex: It is plentiful in urban areas, as it is a popular pet. It has a very fickle nature, purring in happiness one second, then hooking its claws into its trainer's nose. It loves to be admired and pampered.

name: Purugly
pokedex: It becomes wilder and aggressive after evolving. It is known to claim other Pokémon nests as its own. It will make itself appear bigger and glare with piercing eyes to achieve dominance over someone.

name: Chingling
pokedex: It has a ball inside its mouth that makes a ringing sound when it hops around. To defend itself, it will emit low frequency cries that deafen its foes. However this sound is not audible to humans.

name: Stunky
pokedex: Over the years they have moved closer to towns and other human settlements. They release a foul liquid from their rear that stinks for days to scare away predators, but sometimes they do it just for fun.

name: Skuntank
pokedex: It sprays a reeking fluid from its tail. The fluid smells worse the longer it is allowed to fester. It is vulnerable to attacks that come from above due to its exuberant tail. When it is relaxed it doesn't smell bad.

name: Bronzor
pokedex: Genderless. They are found in ancient tombs and temples. Objects shaped like Bronzor have been found within vaults. Bronzors reflect images like mirrors, people say that this reflection shows the future.
evolution_method: It is unknown what triggers its evolution.

name: Bronzong
pokedex: Genderless. Ancient people revered Bronzong for bring the rain and sun at will. One became a news sensation recently when it was dug up at a construction site after a 2000-year-long sleep.

name: Bonsly
pokedex: They thrive in arid places. It looks like it's crying all the time, but it's actually adjusting the moisture of its body and releasing excess water. Over time they become excellent at impersonating trees.
evolution_method: Evolves after learning to Mimic others.

name: Mime Jr.
pokedex: It likes places where people gather and imitates their expressions to try to understand their feelings. It mimics foes, confuses them, then it escapes. It doesn't take long to become a master mime.
evolution_method: Evolves after learning to Mimic others.

name: Happiny
pokedex: It is not common to see Happiny. This baby Pokémon cannot produce eggs yet, so it searches for white stones and carries them in its pouch. It likes to look pretty and tries to always be adorable.

name: Chatot
pokedex: It mimics the cries of other Pokémon to trick them into thinking it's one of them, this way they won't attack it. Chatot that live with humans learn words and phrases, but it's unknown if they really know their meaning.

name: Spiritomb
pokedex: A legend from 500 years ago tells how it got bound into an Odd Keystone after cursing an entire town. Two have been found in recent times. It is said that its vortex has more than 100 haunted souls.

name: Gible
pokedex: It digs tunnels and follows prey while burrowed underground. If you see the fin on its back coming out of the ground it means it is about to attack. It is very aggressive but kind of clumsy. Beware of its big jaws.
evolution_method: Evolves after reaching a certain level.

name: Gabite
pokedex: It hoards a small treasure of sparkly things back in its cave. It will react aggressively toward any potential thief. It is also an excellent hunter, capable of running, swimming and gliding extremely fast.

name: Garchomp
pokedex: Garchomp are scarce in the wild and very dangerous. It folds its arms and uses its fins to fly extremely fast at low heights. Territorial and aggressive it will not rest until it catches any daring trespasser.

name: Munchlax
pokedex: A Munchlax appetite is never really satisfied, it can eat its weight in food and will almost never care about what it is eating. They tend to pick up anything that looks edible and save it for later.

name: Riolu
pokedex: Scarce in the wild, but they have been seen in the mountains. It has the ability to see the auras of others. Through this power it is capable of sensing emotions. It won't get close to those with selfish intentions.

name: Lucario
pokedex: This Pokémon is completely loyal to its trainer. It has the ability not only to see the auras but also to manipulate them into energy. It is also capable of understanding human speech.

name: Hippopotas
pokedex: It lives in arid places where it joins into small groups. It closes its nostrils and submerges under the sand to rest. Females have a different coloration, usually a darker and duller color.
evolution_method: Evolves after reaching a certain level.

name: Hippowdon
pokedex: It becomes territorial and aggressive after evolving. Its open mouth stands over 7 ft tall. There are records of one that came out of the sand and crushed a truck that was passing over its territory.

name: Skorupi
pokedex: It lives in deserts and arid regions. It buries itself under the sand waiting for an unsuspecting prey to come nearby. It will then sting the prey and cling to it tenaciously until the poison takes effect.
evolution_method: Evolves after its poison becomes deadly.

name: Drapion
pokedex: This Pokémon is very aggressive. It can completely rotate its head over its body. Because of this, Drapion has no blind spots. Its venom is deadly and it won't hesitate to use it.

name: Croagunk
pokedex: It is commonly found in marshes. It inflates the sacks on its cheeks and makes croaking sounds. The fluid squeezed from its fingers is poisonous, but it is a common ingredient in medicinal ointments.
evolution_method: Evolves after its poison becomes deadly.

name: Toxicroak
pokedex: The toxin made in its poison sacs is pumped into the knuckle claws through tubes down its arms. Its toxins are so powerful that even a scratch from its knuckles could be fatal in a few hours.

name: Carnivine
pokedex: It binds itself to trees in marshes. It attracts prey with its sweet-smelling drool and gulps them down in one bite. It can take a whole day to digest a single prey, but it won't need to eat for at least a week.

name: Finneon
pokedex: The way its two tail fins flutter while it swims has earned Finneon the nickname "Beautifly of the sea." The line running down its side can store sunlight and glow brightly at night.
evolution_method: Evolves after reaching a certain level.

name: Lumineon
pokedex: It lives in the deep-sea bottom. It attracts prey by flashing the patterns on its tail fins. In the wild it competes against Lanturn for food. Its main predators are Tentacruel and Sharpedo.

name: Mantyke
pokedex: When it swims close to the ocean's surface, people aboard ships are able to observe the pattern on its back as it is different in every region. Mantyke is an intelligent and friendly Pokémon that rarely attacks others.
evolution_method: Evolves when a Remoraid attaches to it.

name: Snover
pokedex: During cold seasons, it migrates to the mountain's lower reaches and returns to the summit in the spring. They are rarely in contact with humans, but are sought for the frozen berries they grow.
evolution_method: Evolves after reaching a certain size.

name: Abomasnow
pokedex: There was a legend for a long time that called this Pokémon "The Ice Monster." Now we know it is a Pokémon that can cover everything around it with deep snow. It likes quiet places and only attacks if provoked.

name: Weavile
pokedex: They live in cold regions, forming groups of four that hunt prey with impressive coordination. They leave claw marks and patterns to indicate their territory. It is devious and loves to cause trouble.

name: Magnezone
pokedex: Genderless. Magneton only evolves into Magnezone in very specific areas of the world. Magnezone has the ability to repel itself from the ground using magnetism. If it is nervous, it pulls all the pieces of metal around it until it relaxes.

name: Lickilicky
pokedex: It uses its tongue as a stretchable arm. It will wrap prey with it and then proceed to eat it. Its saliva causes numbness. Try not to touch its tongue, it might try to eat you by reflex.

name: Rhyperior
pokedex: They have rarely been seen in the wild and only the tallest mountains. It has holes on its hands which are used like cannons to shoot boulders. Be careful, they are very aggressive, but not very smart.
evolution_method: Final Form. It was holding protective gear.

name: Tangrowth
pokedex: While it remains still, it appears to be a large shrub. Unsuspecting prey that wander near get ensnared by its vines. In the summer months, its vines grow so large that you can't even see its eyes.

name: Electivire
pokedex: This Pokémon is reckless and has a short temper. As its electric charge amplifies, blue sparks begin to crackle between its horns. It has registered charge levels of over 20,000 Volts.
evolution_method: Final Form. It was holding an electric charger.

name: Magmortar
pokedex: Magmortar is extremely rare, if you're lucky you can find one living directly on volcanic craters. It raises the temperature of its body at will to the point of bursting into flame. The fire it produces is so hot it is nearly white in color.
evolution_method: Final Form. It was holding molten lava.

name: Togekiss
pokedex: Sightings of these Pokémon have become rare nowadays. They used to visit peaceful regions, bringing with them gifts of kindness and great blessings, but they appear to have vanished in these times of conflict.

name: Yanmega
pokedex: It goes back to its prehistoric roots. It is a lot more violent than its pre-evolved form. Its jaw power is incredible and it is adept at biting apart foes while flying by at high speed. This Pokémon can be brutal.

name: Leafeon
pokedex: Eevee evolves to Leafeon when it's living near a special kind of moss. Its cells are capable of performing photosynthesis. It is a calm Pokémon and does not usually fight but it's leaves are sharp and strong.

name: Glaceon
pokedex: Eevee that are forced to live in freezing temperatures evolve into this Pokémon. It can control its body temperature below zero, freezing its fur and making it extremely tough.
evolution_method: Final Form. Evolved with an Ice Stone.

name: Gliscor
pokedex: Its flight is soundless. It uses its lengthy tail to carry off its prey, then uses its long fangs to do the rest. It is more playful than aggressive, but it is dangerous if you get close to its enormous claws.

name: Mamoswine
pokedex: It was everywhere during the ice age, but its population declined afterwards. This Pokémon uses strong tusks to remove the soil and snow and dig up roots and plants to eat. It has a bad temper.

name: Porygon-Z
pokedex: Genderless. A software to explore another dimension was installed on Porygon. However, it began acting oddly due to glitches in the code. Since then, it has a fondness for videos of Meowth and Skitty on the internet.

name: Gallade
pokedex: This Pokémon is male only. He has an extreme sense of courtesy. In a battle, it uses the blades on his arms as if they were swords. It is a loyal Pokémon, and won't doubt to fiercely protect its trainer.
evolution_method: Final Form. Male Kirilia evolved with a Shiny Stone.

name: Probopass
pokedex: It exudes strong magnetism from all over. It controls three small units called Mini-Noses that float around it and act is arms. It usually stays motionless unless attacked or provoked.

name: Dusknoir
pokedex: This feared Pokémon is said to travel to the other world. Some even believe that it takes lost spirits along with it. It uses the antenna on its head to receive messages from the deceased.
evolution_method: Final Form. It was holding the grim reaper's clothes.

name: Froslass
pokedex: This Pokémon is female only. Legends in the snowy regions say that a woman who was lost on an icy mountain was reborn as Froslass. It appears during blizzards to take lost people away.

name: Rotom
pokedex: Genderless. Its electric-like body can enter some kinds of machines and take control of them in order to cause mischief. It changes its form to that of the electric appliance, allowing it to become more powerful.

name: Rotom Dex
pokedex: A Pokedex possessed by a Rotom. It has access to all the information inside the computer and uses the sounds to emulate speech. While in this form it can use the move Light Screen.

name: Rotom Fan
pokedex: A Desk Fan possessed by a Rotom. It uses Wind powers and scatters everything around with terrible air currents. While in this form it can use the move: Air Slash

name: Rotom Frost
pokedex: A refrigerator possessed by a Rotom. It uses Ice powers, traps people inside and freezes them in solid ice blocks. While in this form it can use the move: Blizzard.

name: Rotom Heat
pokedex: A Microwave possessed by a Rotom. It uses fire powers and burns the food of unsuspecting people. While in this form it can use the move Overheat.

name: Rotom Mow
pokedex: A Lawnmower possessed by a Rotom. It uses Grass powers, mows awful patterns in the grass and chases people with the blades out. While in this form it can use the move: Leaf Storm.

name: Rotom Wash
pokedex: A Washing Machine possessed by a Rotom. It uses Water powers and floods the houses with torrents of water. While in this form it can use the move: Hydro Pump.

name: Uxie
pokedex: In the myths of Sinnoh, they talk about three beings that come from the same egg. The yellow one was the being of knowledge. Together they shaped the human race to be complete.

name: Mesprit
pokedex: In the myths of Sinnoh, they talk about three beings that come from the same egg. The pink one was the being of emotion. Together they shaped the human race to be complete.

name: Azelf
pokedex: In the myths of Sinnoh, they talk about three beings that come from the same egg. The blue one was the being of willpower. Together they shaped the human race to be complete.

name: Dialga
pokedex: In some religions there is a being called "The god of Time" whose first roar brought future, present, and past.

name: Palkia
pokedex: A fantasy book describes a place where space bends in impossible ways and the master of that site was a Pokémon with a similar appearance.

name: Heatran
pokedex: An old painting showed a similar Pokémon standing atop an erupting Volcano.

name: Regigigas
pokedex: A very old legend tells about the King of Giants, who could crush a mountain with its grip and mold living titans from the rubble.

name: Cresselia
pokedex: The embodiment of dreams comes to life during the crescent moon nights. You will be blessed with peaceful bedtimes if you keep one of its feathers. Or so they say.

name: Phione
pokedex: There have been sightings of small groups of similar Pokémon but its existence has never been confirmed. It is said to be the offspring of Manaphy.

name: Manaphy
pokedex: It is said that after the war for land and sea was over, a tiny Pokémon was born from the bottom of the ocean to bond with all the creatures as a sign of peace.

name: Darkrai
pokedex: All around the world young children have depicted a similar figure in their drawings. They call it, "The Boogeyman". People say it will make all your nightmares come true.

name: Shaymin (land)
pokedex: There are old traces of gigantic trees that once grew all over the earth. They were called the "Trees of Life" and their flowers granted the power of flight to the kind-hearted or so the legend says.

name: Shaymin (sky)
pokedex: There are old traces of gigantic trees that once grew all over the earth. They were called the "Trees of Life" and their flowers granted the power of flight to the kind-hearted or so the legend says.

name: Victini
pokedex: On tournament days, Trainers at a "V" shaped apple as a sign of good luck. It is unknown if it has anything to do with this Pokémon.

name: Snivy
pokedex: It is very intelligent and independent, although it seems calm it doesn't like being bossed around. Being exposed to lots of sunlight makes its movements swifter. The tail drops if it is not feeling well.
evolution_method: Evolves after reaching a certain level.

name: Servine
pokedex: It moves along the ground by sliding. Its swift movements befuddle its foes, then attacks with a vine whip. It always keeps itself clean and it demands care from its trainer, otherwise it will misbehave.
evolution_method: Evolves after reaching a certain level.

name: Serperior
pokedex: It stops enemies dead in their tracks with just one intense glare. It is a noble and proud Pokémon. It is not aggressive, but it can be very stubborn. It takes a really strong foe for it to take the fight seriously.

name: Tepig
pokedex: It blows fire through its nose. When it catches a cold, the fire becomes pitch-black smoke instead. Tepig loves to eat roasted berries and its keen sense of smell allows it to find them easily.
evolution_method: Evolves after reaching a certain level.

name: Pignite
pokedex: Whatever it eats becomes fuel for the flame on its stomach. When it is angered, the intensity of the flame increases. It is not common to see them in the wild. They are mostly found living in warm places.
evolution_method: Evolves after reaching a certain level.

name: Emboar
pokedex: Although it has a scary exterior, it is a very gentle Pokémon that cares deeply for family and friends. It can set its punches and beard on fire, it also shows proficiency in martial arts like Judo.

name: Oshawott
pokedex: It is only seen close to the sea in a few places in the world. Oshawott uses the scallop in on its chest as a tool for multiple purposes and as a weapon to slash and fight. It is small, but brave and daring.
evolution_method: Evolves after reaching a certain level.

name: Dewott
pokedex: It isolates itself from others and trains every day to perform a double scallop slash technique. This Pokémon takes itself very seriously and won't back down from any challenge.
evolution_method: Evolves after reaching a certain level.

name: Samurott
pokedex: It uses the horn on its head and both scimitars attached to its front legs as weapons. In the late spring and fall, they gather on cold beaches and fight each other. The winner lets out an intimidating roar.

name: Patrat
pokedex: They live in grass fields in big groups. One of them is always looking out for predators. The group gathers food they store in their cheeks to bring it back home. They are wary and alert at all times.

name: Watchog
pokedex: Their fur has a luminescent property. They make the patterns on their bodies glow in order to threaten predators. Their keen eyesight allows them to see in the dark. They are also good diggers.

name: Lillipup
pokedex: Good with children and old people, this gentle Pokémon is a favorite to keep as a pet. It is very brave and smart and will protect its trainer against any threat. It uses the hair on its head to feel its surroundings.

name: Herdier
pokedex: It loyally follows its Trainer's orders. For ages, they have helped Trainers to raise well behaved Pokémon. It has black, cape-like fur that is very hard and keeps it protected from the weather.

name: Stoutland
pokedex: For many years, this Pokémon has helped with rescue missions in hostile places. Its outer coat is hard on the exterior, but soft and silky on the inside. They keep people safe and warm while help is on the way.

name: Purrloin
pokedex: They have adapted to live in the streets of big cities. They steal for fun, but their victims can't help but forgive them. Their cute act is a ruse. People who keep them as pets often regret it.
evolution_method: Evolves be being surrounded by riches.

name: Liepard
pokedex: It's difficult to see one in the wild. These Pokémon vanish and appear attacking unexpectedly. Many trainers are drawn to their beautiful fur and elegant appeal, but they can be quite dangerous.

name: Pansage
pokedex: Pansage is a friendly Pokémon. It is good at finding berries and will share them with other Pokémon. The leaves on its head have medicinal properties. If it finds a sick Pokémon, it will offer some to heal it.

name: Simisage
pokedex: It becomes somewhat ill tempered after it evolves. The leaves on its head can be made into a bitter, but effective medicine. However, it will attack anyone trying to take them with its thorned tail.

name: Pansear
pokedex: It lives close to volcanic mountains. It is very intelligent, it roasts berries before eating them and helps lost people. When angered the tuft of hair on its head and tail can burst into flames.

name: Simisear
pokedex: A flame burns on top of its head. It scatters embers from its head and tail to sear its opponents. It loves sweets and is not afraid to go near humans to try to get some candy by begging or by stealing.

name: Panpour
pokedex: It does not thrive in dry climates. It keeps itself damp by shooting the water stored in its head tuft. Its water is valued by gardeners and Grass Pokémon breeders as it makes plants grow beautiful.

name: Simipour
pokedex: It prefers places with clean water. When its tuft runs low, it replenishes it by siphoning water up with its tail. It is said that if you see a Simipour swimming in a pond, the water is safe to drink.

name: Munna
pokedex: It lurks close to towns and eats the dreams of people and Pokémon. When it eats a pleasant dream, it expels pink-colored mist. If you forgot what you dreamed, a Munna must have eaten your dream.

name: Musharna
pokedex: It communicates with the mist on its forehead, it can create shapes and images from dreams it has eaten. It is said that this Pokémon is a link between this world and another one made entirely of dreams.

name: Pidove
pokedex: These Pokémon thrive in the cities. They are accustomed to people and often gather in the parks. They are forgetful and not very smart, but they always remember the way back home.
evolution_method: Evolves after reaching a certain level.

name: Tranquill
pokedex: During war and old times people made use of Tranquill's sense of location to send letters. It will never fail to find its way back home. They like quiet forests and enjoy to relax in the peace and quiet.
evolution_method: Evolves after reaching a certain level.

name: Unfezant
pokedex: Males swing the beautiful plumage on their heads to threaten others and to court females. Although less visually appealing, females are better at flying. Once they form a pair they are mated for life.

name: Blitzle
pokedex: When storm clouds cover the plains you can see them running around chasing the lightnings to absorb them on their mane. They form big herds and use the pattern on their skin to confuse predators.
evolution_method: Evolves after reaching a certain level.

name: Zebstrika
pokedex: It is very ill tempered and wild, there have been very few cases of it being successfully tamed. It can shoot lightning from its mane in all directions. If you try to mount it without warning, it will shock you.

name: Roggenrola
pokedex: It is made from compressed rock, making its body almost as hard as steel. It is blind. What looks like its eye is really an ear, for this reason it can live in the darkest of caves, feeding on rocks to grow stronger.
evolution_method: Evolves after reaching a certain level.

name: Boldore
pokedex: It releases the excess of its energy in the form of red crystals. It is still blind, so it looks for water sources inside underground caves by using echolocation. It is a passive creature that keeps to itself most of the time.

name: Gigalith
pokedex: It is a serious Pokémon that doesn't interact with others too much. It uses the sharp crystals in its body to recharge using the sun's energy. If angered, it can bury its foe under giant rock slides or explode at will.

name: Woobat
pokedex: It lives in the dark forests and caves. It emits ultrasonic waves from its nose to learn about its surroundings. The two small eyes it has gets covered by its own fur. It clings to trees and cave walls to sleep at night.

name: Swoobat
pokedex: They communicate by emitting ultrasonic waves through their noses. The sound is not perceived by humans, but it can affect their moods and emotions. It hunts Bug Pokémon and loves fresh fruit.

name: Drilbur
pokedex: They can be found in caves and wreaking havoc on vegetable farms. It makes its way swiftly through the soil by putting both claws together and rotating at high speed. It is friendly and not afraid of humans.
evolution_method: Evolves by drilling had stone regularly.

name: Excadrill
pokedex: They build maze-like nests deep underground. Humans make use of their drilling abilities to dig tunnels for subway trains. This Pokémon does not back out from foes and can be a formidable opponent.

name: Audino
pokedex: Its auditory sense is astounding, using the feelers on its ears it can know the health state of others. It is a caring Pokémon with a sweet disposition to help, but it is not too common to see in the wild.

name: Noibat
pokedex: They live in dark caves and use echolocation to move around. Their enourmous ears can emit ultrasonic waves that can cause dizziness. Groups of them can even take prey several times their size.

name: Noivern
pokedex: They fly during the new moon and attack careless prey. Nothing can beat them in a battle in teh dark. To keep them calm you should feed them fruit or else they'll release shocking ulttrasonic waves.
